NK009(ta)003:1566: tha ma sum cha tshang ba dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:1567: yang na bka' blo bde ba /
NK009(ta)003:1570: sgrub pa po la dad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1577: thal skyel me len chu 'chu ba de'o //
NK009(ta)003:1579: g.yos sogs bya ba byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1583: bsnyen sgrub ji lta ba shes pa des /
NK009(ta)003:1584: rang khams ma bde na thun mi chag pa dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:1586: nam dga' dga' dang ci thod thod gtam 'chal du gzhug pas 'grub bam zhe na /
NK009(ta)003:1593: ra ba bzhi la bsnyen pa'i dus //
NK009(ta)003:1594: 'bring po bzhi la sgrub pa'i dus //
NK009(ta)003:1595: tha chung bzhi la las sbyor bya //
NK009(ta)003:1597: yang zla stod thams cad bzlog pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:1598: zla smad thams cad thebs pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:1599: zhes pa dang khyad par du //
NK009(ta)003:1600: ra ba bzhi la gdab las ldog /
NK009(ta)003:1601: 'bring po bzhi la zor las ldog /
NK009(ta)003:1602: tha chung bzhi la las dag bya //
NK009(ta)003:1606: dpyid zla gsum la brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1611: shar dang de bzhin shar lhor blta'o //
NK009(ta)003:1612: dbyar zla gsum la brdeg pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:1617: nub byang byang shar kha blta'o //
NK009(ta)003:1618: ston zla gsum la brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1623: byang shar byang dang nub tu blta'o //
NK009(ta)003:1624: dgun zla gsum pa brdeg pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1629: byang dang lho ru kha blta'o //
NK009(ta)003:1630: dpyid zla gsum la ldog pa'i dus //
NK009(ta)003:1635: dbyar zla gsum la bzlog pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1642: ston zla gsum la ldog pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1647: dgun zla gsum la ldog pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:1653: skar ma smel po dang mgo /
NK009(ta)003:1655: nyi ma bdud kyi nyi ma drag po la gtad do //
NK009(ta)003:1656: bsnyen pa la gza' skar gang bzang la bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1657: lnga pa rdzas dang yo byad rten dang rdzas med
NK009(ta)003:1658: kyang sgrub tu rung ngam zhe na mi rung ste
NK009(ta)003:1659: / phun sum tshogs pa la lnga ste /
NK009(ta)003:1661: rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad /
NK009(ta)003:1663: thugs dam bskang ba'i yo byad /
NK009(ta)003:1664: dgra bgegs gsod pa'i yo byad do //
NK009(ta)003:1665: dang po 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad ni /
NK009(ta)003:1666: rten dang rdzas mi gtsang bas sgrub tu rung ngam zhes na mi rung ste /
NK009(ta)003:1669: btung ba sgrub dus dang sbyar te ldong thabs su bskyed dgos te /
NK009(ta)003:1670: brgya lam gal te ma 'grub na spogs chog dgos pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1671: gnyis pa rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:1678: sngon du sgrub khang btsan po rgyan dang ldan pa /
NK009(ta)003:1683: mdzod chung dang ldan par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1689: sgyogs the rang rkang dang ldan par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1690: gnyis pa bgegs bzlog pa la sreg rdzas dang /
NK009(ta)003:1701: 'khor lo'i rdzas rnams tshud par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1702: gnyis pa nang gi rkyen bzlog pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:1703: nad 'dus pa las gyur pa bzlog pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:1704: nyon mongs pa rang dbang med par bzlog pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1707: tshad pa la bsil sman dang /
NK009(ta)003:1708: grang ba la drod sman dang /
NK009(ta)003:1709: mkhris pa la lca sga dang bu ram /
NK009(ta)003:1710: nad 'dus pa la sman thams cad tshang bar bya /
NK009(ta)003:1713: spra ba la sogs pa gsog go //
NK009(ta)003:1714: gnyis pa nyon mongs pa langs na /
NK009(ta)003:1718: yang na chos thams cad rang bzhin med par shes par byas la /
NK009(ta)003:1719: bla ma'i snyan brgyud zab mo thos pa tsam gyis grol ba /
NK009(ta)003:1720: bsgom pa tsam gyis byin rlabs 'byung ba sta gon du bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1721: gsum pa lha sgrub pa'i yo byad la /
NK009(ta)003:1722: brag btsan po'am sa bzang po la sgrub khang btsan po byas la /
NK009(ta)003:1723: de'i dbus su dkyil 'khor 'dom gang gru bzhi pa brtsigs te dpangs khru gang ba /
NK009(ta)003:1724: der yang dur khrod du sgrub par bya ba'i phyir
NK009(ta)003:1725: thod tshal la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa bris la
NK009(ta)003:1726: gzhug / longs spyod che bar bya ba'i phyir rat+na lnga dang 'bru sna lnga gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1727: nad nyung bar bya ba'i phyir sman lnga gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1728: grags pa thob par bya ba'i phyir dri lnga gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1729: bum gter bcug la me long gi ngos 'dra bar bya /
NK009(ta)003:1730: de yang shar mtho na nor la gzan /
NK009(ta)003:1732: nub mtho na srog la gzan /
NK009(ta)003:1733: byang mtho na rigs rgyud chad /
NK009(ta)003:1734: dbus mtho na rang la ngan /
NK009(ta)003:1736: de'i zur bzhi srung ma'i stegs bu dpangs sor bzhi /
NK009(ta)003:1737: rgyar khru re yod pa bzhi brtseg par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1738: de nas dal gyi dbus su mi'i keng rus barla
NK009(ta)003:1739: dang rje ngar du bcas pa rkang mthil gyen la
NK009(ta)003:1740: bstan pa'i khri'u chen po gcig bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:1741: de'i steng du lce spyang gi khog pa'am /
NK009(ta)003:1743: de'i nang du sha sna snying sna 'bru sna las byas pa'i dpal chen po'i dkyil gtor bya /
NK009(ta)003:1744: de'i steng du 'bar ba'i lha tshogs bskyed la zas phud btung phud lo'am mi rabs su 'bul /
NK009(ta)003:1745: thun mtshams kyi bzlas pa la gzhol /
NK009(ta)003:1746: tshil chen gyi sprin khebs bya /
NK009(ta)003:1747: rma bya'i gdugs phub la bzhag go //
NK009(ta)003:1748: de'i g.yas su gta' gtor bzang du bsham /
NK009(ta)003:1751: zla ba re la kha bran /
NK009(ta)003:1752: g.yon nam rgyab tu gtor ma gsum bca' /
NK009(ta)003:1753: phyi'i lha mo lngar bskyed pa phyi'i gtor ma /
NK009(ta)003:1754: nang gi lha mo lngar bskyed pa nang gi gtor ma /
NK009(ta)003:1755: 'dod yon lha mo lngar bskyed pa gsang ba'i gtor ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:1756: mdun du gtso bo'i 'gying phur gdan dang bcas pa dar mthing gi cod pan btags pa gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1757: de'i sngon du lha phur lnga bcu rtsa gcig thod pa nas kyis bkang bar gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1758: gzhan yang gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK009(ta)003:1761: phur pa sil bu rnams gsog go //
NK009(ta)003:1762: zur gyi srung ma'i stegs bur rang rang gi dam rdzas dang /
NK009(ta)003:1764: de'ang lhor shar gyi stegs bur shwa na ma'i rdzas /
NK009(ta)003:1766: dam rdzas yod na shugs kyis 'du /
NK009(ta)003:1767: rang shugs su las byed do //
NK009(ta)003:1768: spyang khu 'phar ba wa dang khyi //
NK009(ta)003:1769: shwa na ma yi rdzas su bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1770: mar khu zhag dang 'o ma khrag /
NK009(ta)003:1772: bse mo bzhi yi rdzas su bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1773: mda' dar stag ras nub byang du /
NK009(ta)003:1775: skyes bu ging gi rdzas su bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1777: lug nag rta nag nal bu'i sha /
NK009(ta)003:1778: re ma t+ai yi rdzas su bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1781: dbus su khri'u'i steng du bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1782: dza gad rak+tasa mtha' ma bskor //
NK009(ta)003:1783: zhes pas bsreg rdzas thams cad shar lho me lhar bsham /
NK009(ta)003:1784: mnan rdzas thams cad lho nub srin por /
NK009(ta)003:1785: zor rdzas nub byang rlung lhar /
NK009(ta)003:1786: thun rdzas byang shar dbang ldan du /
NK009(ta)003:1787: mchod rdzas thams cad rang gi mdun du bsham /
NK009(ta)003:1788: srog la 'khor lo bskor ba lho nub tu bsham mo //
NK009(ta)003:1789: bzhi pa thugs dam bskang ba'i yo byad ni /
NK009(ta)003:1790: gnas der zhing chen gyi bla bre /
NK009(ta)003:1791: zhing chung gi za ra tshags /
NK009(ta)003:1793: b+han+d+ha skam rlon gyi tsha tshar /
NK009(ta)003:1794: rgyu ma bus pa'i barla rgyan /
NK009(ta)003:1800: zhal zas tshogs kyi gtor ma mchod pa zer ba'ang snang /
NK009(ta)003:1803: lnga pa dgra bgegs bsad pa'i rdzas ni /
NK009(ta)003:1804: srog la 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:1806: de'i 'brub khung gru gsum pa bcas ste /
NK009(ta)003:1809: so so yin te mi gcig go //
NK009(ta)003:1810: ling+ga dang ni nya bo gnyis //
NK009(ta)003:1811: dmigs pa gcig ste rgyu mi gcig /
NK009(ta)003:1812: ling+ga nya bo'i snying gar gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1814: zan la nya bo bca' ste /
NK009(ta)003:1816: grog mkhar sa dang rkang rjes sa //
NK009(ta)003:1817: phyi sa dri chu gos dum rnams //
NK009(ta)003:1818: nya bo bya ba'i rdzas su bshad //
NK009(ta)003:1819: shun chen gro ga shog shog rnams //
NK009(ta)003:1820: ling+ga bri ba'i rdzas su bshad //
NK009(ta)003:1821: ces pa'i rgyu rkyen drug la /
NK009(ta)003:1822: phar rkan tshur rkan rkang rjes sa /
NK009(ta)003:1834: lha khang dang mchod rten rnying pa'i sa /
NK009(ta)003:1836: mi phung sa rnams la nya bo rus shing dag bcas pa bya /
NK009(ta)003:1837: khrag nad gtong ba'i phyir khrag sna gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1838: dug nad gtong ba'i phyir dug sna gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1839: nad tshad pa gtong ba'i phyir drod sman gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1840: grir bsad pa'i phyir gri gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1841: 'dre la byed na rten gyis gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1842: lder bzo byas la ming rus ling+ga'i snying gar gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:1843: gnyis pa ling+ga bri ba la /
NK009(ta)003:1845: dus dang bri mkhan snag tsha gsum //
NK009(ta)003:1846: dus ni smin drug sa 'og dus //
NK009(ta)003:1847: 'bri mkhan rang bzhin yon tan can //
NK009(ta)003:1848: snag tsha dme khrag gsum gyis byas //
NK009(ta)003:1849: rgyal po la ni rkyang khru'o //
NK009(ta)003:1851: skyes pa la ni mtho gang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:1852: bud med la ni mdzub gang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:1853: byis pa la ni sor bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:1855: de la ling+ga tsakra 'bri dus su kha rlangs mi btang /
NK009(ta)003:1862: sngags pa dpral bar ha sa bri /
NK009(ta)003:1863: lte bar a we sha bri /
NK009(ta)003:1864: yan lag la sh+ri kri bri /
NK009(ta)003:1865: lce la dz+wa la pa ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1866: spyi bor ta tha ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1868: lam h+aum lam gyis mtha' bskor /
NK009(ta)003:1869: rtsibs thams cad du 'dus pa bri /
NK009(ta)003:1871: de'i mthar srung ma'i sngags kyis bskor ro //
NK009(ta)003:1872: gtad byed pa'i mdze thod la dpral ba sh+ri kri bri /
NK009(ta)003:1873: spyi bor ta tha ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1874: rna bar bi da ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1875: ltag par ha sa ya ra bri /
NK009(ta)003:1876: mgrin par a we sha ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1877: rkan la dz+wa la pa ya bri //
NK009(ta)003:1879: bgegs gnon pa'i khyi thod la /
NK009(ta)003:1880: smin mtshams su ha sa bri /
NK009(ta)003:1883: rkan la dz+wa la ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1884: spyi bor ta tha ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1885: ma mkhal la bi da ya bri /
NK009(ta)003:1889: gzas pa po dngos su gsal ba /
NK009(ta)003:1890: 'brub khung dregs pa'i zhal du gsal ba /
NK009(ta)003:1891: rtsang phur pa'i srung mar gsal ba /
NK009(ta)003:1892: thun khrag mtshon char gsal ba /
NK009(ta)003:1893: thun brgyabs pas khong khrag lud nas myags myags song bar bsam mo //
NK009(ta)003:1894: nya bo de'i lus kyi gnas bcur khro bo bcu'i phur pa bcu btab la bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1895: lus kyi mtsho bzhi la sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa bzhi btab /
NK009(ta)003:1896: gnam gyi 'ju thag bcad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:1897: sa yi rten phur phyung ba rnams su phur pa drug btab la bzhag /
NK009(ta)003:1898: de yang bsnyen dus su gan rkyal mgo phar bstan du bya /
NK009(ta)003:1899: sgrub dus su kha sbub mgo tshur bstan no //
NK009(ta)003:1900: de rnams shin tu gal che ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:1901: sgrub pa las kyi gzhi bzung ba tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:1902: spyi don gnyis pa dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum sngon
NK009(ta)003:1903: du 'gro ba phrin las kyi rim pa dang bcas
NK009(ta)003:1904: te don gyi khog dbub pa la /
NK009(ta)003:1906: sngon du 'gro ba dang dal gsum dngos su //
NK009(ta)003:1914: rnam gsum byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1915: de rnams ni zhi khro la sogs pa phrin las spyi'i sngon du 'gro ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:1916: de la dang po 'bar ba mtshams kyi dal gyis mtshams bcad pa la mdo gsum /
NK009(ta)003:1918: yan lag de rnams mi shes na mtshams gcod la mi re'o //
NK009(ta)003:1920: de la dang po mdo gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:1921: re re la'ang gsum gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:1922: rtsa ba brgyad po gang zhe na /
NK009(ta)003:1923: dang po mtshams gcod mkhan gyi rten gyi gang zag gsum dgos pas gang gis bcad /
NK009(ta)003:1924: gang bcad rgyu'i mi mthun phyogs las gang bcad /
NK009(ta)003:1925: mtshams bcad pa'i don gyi ngo bo gsum po gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:1926: de la mtshams kyi gzhung chen po gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:1927: gzhung de gsum la gang nas bshad kyi khungs gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:1928: mtshams bcad pa'i gnas skabs su 'bras bu gsum ji ltar 'byung /
NK009(ta)003:1929: mtshams re re la gsum gsum re dbye ba dgu yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:1930: mtshams bcad pa la 'bras bu rnam pa gsum po ci ltar 'byung ba yin /
NK009(ta)003:1932: de la dang po gang zag gsum ni rab lta ba rtogs pa /
NK009(ta)003:1934: tha ma slob pa res 'jog pa'i gang zag go //
NK009(ta)003:1935: de yang gang zag rab des snang ba chos skur rtogs pas spang blang med par mtshams bcad zin /
NK009(ta)003:1936: 'bring des snang ba lhar rtogs pas 'dre med de bcad zin //
NK009(ta)003:1937: tha ma de la ma bcad na 'dre 'ong /
NK009(ta)003:1938: bcad na 'dre mi 'ong bas bcad dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:1939: gnyis pa bcad rgyu mi mthun pa ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:1942: gsang ba rnam rtogs phra rags so //
NK009(ta)003:1943: gsum pa mtshams bcad kyi ngo bo ni /
NK009(ta)003:1946: sngags dang phyag rgyas srung mtshams so //
NK009(ta)003:1947: bzhi pa de gsum po gzhung chen po gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:1948: lta ba la me khrag 'chol ba'i mtshams /
NK009(ta)003:1949: bskyed rim la khro bo 'chol ba'i mtshams /
NK009(ta)003:1950: sngags dang phyag rgya la mtshon cha 'chol ba'i mtshams so //
NK009(ta)003:1951: lnga pa gang nas bshad kyi khungs gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:1952: me khrag 'chol ba ma gshin gyi rgyud nas bshad /
NK009(ta)003:1953: khro bo 'chol ba zhi khro'i rgyud nas bshad /
NK009(ta)003:1954: mtshon cha 'chol ba yang phur gyi rgyud nas bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:1955: drug pa gnas skabs kyi dgos pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:1956: phyi mtshams bcad pas g.yeng ba zhi /
NK009(ta)003:1957: nang mtshams bcad pa'i bar mi chad /
NK009(ta)003:1958: gsang mtshams bcad pas sems chos skur gnas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1959: bdun pa dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:1960: snang ba mi'i mtshams bcad pa /
NK009(ta)003:1961: mi snang ba bgegs kyi mtshams bcad pa /
NK009(ta)003:1962: phra ba rnam par rtog pa'i mtshams bcad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1964: yul dpon la bka' phog pa /
NK009(ta)003:1965: nga yi rten sgrub ma thon par 'tshe ba ma btang zhig ces bka' basgo'o //
NK009(ta)003:1966: gnyis pa mi snang ba la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:1971: phyi'i phyi mtshams su gser skyems btang zhing bden pa bdar /
NK009(ta)003:1972: phyi'i nang mtshams su rgyal chen bzhi'i tho bzhi gzug /
NK009(ta)003:1973: phyi'i gsang mtshams su khro bo bcu'i phur pa gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1975: nang gi phyi mtshams su gshin rje gshed kyi sgo byang phyi sgo la gdags /
NK009(ta)003:1976: nang gi nang mtshams su bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sgo byang nang sgo la gdags /
NK009(ta)003:1977: nang gi gsang mtshams su dam sri them 'og tu mnan pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:1979: gsang mtshams kyi phyi mtshams su gnas srung khro bo bcur bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:1980: gsang mtshams gyi nang mtshams su bdag srung rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:1981: gsang mtshams kyi gsang mtshams su lha dang bgegs la bka' bsgo ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:1982: brgyad pa 'bras bu ni sku gsum thob ste /
NK009(ta)003:1984: de ltar so so la gsum gsum ste yan lag
NK009(ta)003:1985: sum cu rtsa gsum ma shes par mtshams gcod la
NK009(ta)003:1986: mi theng ngo // 'bar ba mtshams kyi dal tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:1987: gnyis pa brda sgo dbye ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:1988: dal gyi shar phyogs kyi sgo phye ste bltas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:1989: gtso bo nas sgo ma'i bar du bltas pas zhal thal ler mthong bar bsgoms la /
NK009(ta)003:1992: bdag dang dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lha tshogs gnyis //
NK009(ta)003:1993: ye'am gdod nas gnyis su med pa las //
NK009(ta)003:1994: bdag cag ma rig 'khrul pas bsgribs pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:1995: log rtog mtshan ma'i rtog pa'i sprin gyis bsgribs //
NK009(ta)003:1996: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs zhal yang ma mthong bas //
NK009(ta)003:1997: bdag 'jug dkyil 'khor sgo 'di dbye ru gsol //
NK009(ta)003:1998: ma rig mun pa'i tshogs kyi bar chod pas //
NK009(ta)003:1999: thugs rje nyi zla'i 'od kyis bsal du gsol //
NK009(ta)003:2000: ku m+aa ra dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa man+da la sarba
NK009(ta)003:2001: de wa ma h+aa ka ru ni ka sa ma
NK009(ta)003:2002: ya hoh pra we sha phata /
NK009(ta)003:2004: de nas gsum pa rtogs pa brda'i phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:2006: chos sku bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK009(ta)003:2007: longs sku phyogs bcu khro rgyal dkyil 'khor dang //
NK009(ta)003:2008: sprul sku badz+ra 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK009(ta)003:2009: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum 'bar ba'i sras mchog la //
NK009(ta)003:2010: rjes su yi rang shin tu ngo mtshar che ba yis //
NK009(ta)003:2011: phyag brgya brda dang gar gyi sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK009(ta)003:2012: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa man+da
NK009(ta)003:2013: la sarba de wa a k+aa ro ma mi na
NK009(ta)003:2014: mo zhes brjod / de nas bzhi pa rtags gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2015: mched lcam rnams gral byas la /
NK009(ta)003:2016: ye shes lha'i rtags su rak+ta'i thig le sna rtse 'khur tshos gnyis mtho sar gdab /
NK009(ta)003:2017: thal chen gi tshom bu ni spyi gtsug mgrin pa
NK009(ta)003:2018: snying gar byas pa la dpral bar kha t+w+aam ka
NK009(ta)003:2019: bri / zhag gi zo ris ni snying gar zla phyed rdo rje bri /
NK009(ta)003:2020: de nas rdo rje'i gral byas /
NK009(ta)003:2022: de nas lnga pa nyams chag sgrib sbyangs gi dal la bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:2025: yan lag sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK009(ta)003:2026: dang po mdo bzhi ni re re la bzhi bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2028: dang po bshags mkhan gyi rten gyi gang zag bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2029: bshags rgyu'i sdig pa bzhi gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2030: bshags pa'i yul bzhi po gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2031: bshags pa'i ru chen bzhi bya ba gang yin //
NK009(ta)003:2032: bshags pa'i gzhung chen po bzhi bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2033: de la mdzad mkhan gyi slob dpon bzhi bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2034: bshags pa'i dgos ched bzhi bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2035: bshags pa'i thabs bzhi bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2036: dang po gang zag bzhi las /
NK009(ta)003:2037: dang po skyabs 'gro'i sdom pa thob pa dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2038: de nas sems bskyed thob pa dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2039: de nas dbang bskur thob pa dang gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2040: de nas bskyed rdzogs shes pa dang ldan pas bshags dgos te /
NK009(ta)003:2041: tha mal pas ni ye nyams chen po yin pas bshags chag chad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2042: gnyis pa bshags rgyu'i sdig pa la'ang bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:2043: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2044: so sor thar ba'i sdom pa shor ba dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2045: byang sems kyi sems bskyed shor ba dang gsum //
NK009(ta)003:2046: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa dang bzhi po bshags dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:2047: gsum pa bshags pa'i yul bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:2048: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bla ma dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2049: dngos grub ster ba'i yi dam lha dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2050: thugs rjes skyob pa'i bde bar gshegs pa dang gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2051: legs nyes stangs 'dzin gyi ma mo mkha' 'gro dang bzhi la bshags dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:2052: bzhi pa bshags pa'i ru chen bzhi la /
NK009(ta)003:2053: rtogs pa lta bu'i sgo nas bshags pa dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2054: sgom pa bskyed rdzogs kyi sgo nas bshags pas dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2055: bsrung bya dam tshig gi sgo nas bshags pa dang gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2056: gdung ba smre sngags kyi sgo nas bshags pa dang bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2057: lnga pa de la gzhung chen po bzhi yod de /
NK009(ta)003:2058: lta ba la ma mo'i klong bshags dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2059: bskyed rdzogs la ye shes sku mchog dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2060: bsrung bya la dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa dang gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2061: smre sngags la ye shes mkha' 'gro'i bshags pa dang bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2062: drug pa mdzad mkhan bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:2063: bram ze mi'i thod pa can gyis lta ba'i klong bshags mdzad /
NK009(ta)003:2064: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches ye shes sku mchog mdzad /
NK009(ta)003:2065: rje ti tra ma tis dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa mdzad /
NK009(ta)003:2066: a tsar+ya gnyan dpal dbyangs kyis ye shes mkha' 'gro'i bshags pa mdzad do //
NK009(ta)003:2067: bdun pa dgos ched bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:2068: yang dag don gyi gcugs sbyang ba la lta ba'i klong bshags /
NK009(ta)003:2069: lha dang mi'i gcugs sbyang ba la ye shes sku mchog /
NK009(ta)003:2070: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi gcugs sbyang ba la dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa /
NK009(ta)003:2071: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro'i gcugs sbyang ba la ye shes mkha' 'gro'i bshags pa mdzad do //
NK009(ta)003:2072: brgyad pa bshags thabs bzhi la /
NK009(ta)003:2073: lta ba seng ge'i nga ros rang bzhin med par byas te bshags /
NK009(ta)003:2074: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mes bsregs te bshags /
NK009(ta)003:2075: spyod pa glang po che'i chus bkrus te bshags /
NK009(ta)003:2076: gdung ba'i smre sngags dbyangs dang bcas bshags pa dang bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2077: sgos bshags ni rang rang gi ci rigs par thong ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2078: de nas drug pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2079: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab pas
NK009(ta)003:2080: rtsa ba'i bla ma de la brgyud pa'i bla ma
NK009(ta)003:2081: dang / dpa' bo dpa' mo 'bum gyis bskor bar nam mkhar thibs se byon par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2082: de 'og rigs lnga gdan tsho lnga la dus gsum gyi bud+d+hasa bskor ba rnams byon /
NK009(ta)003:2083: de'i 'og rig 'dzin 'bum phrag du ma la ma mo mkha' 'gros bskor ba byon par bsam la /
NK009(ta)003:2084: sa ma ya hoh byas pas yum rnams kyis bskul /
NK009(ta)003:2085: sa ma ya s+t+wam byas pas yab rnams kyis gnang ste sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK009(ta)003:2086: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems bdud rtsi babs pa bdag gi spyi gtsug tu thim /
NK009(ta)003:2087: lus ngag gi sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2088: a la la hoh zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:2091: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK009(ta)003:2092: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK009(ta)003:2093: sgrub mchog bdag la dbang cig bskur //
NK009(ta)003:2094: gnas mchog 'di ru byin cig phob //
NK009(ta)003:2095: ces brjod cing rol mo'i sgra btang /
NK009(ta)003:2096: gsur chen gyi dud pa btang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2097: bdun pa byin rlabs rnam gsum gyi dal la mdo gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2099: yan lag sum cu rtsa bdun no //
NK009(ta)003:2100: mdo gsum re re la'ang gsum gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:2102: gang gis byin gyis brlabs pa gsum bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2103: gang du bshams pa'i snod rnam pa gsum bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2104: gang bshags pa'i dngos po gsum bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2105: gang gis sbyangs pa'i sbyong byed gsum ni gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2106: gang bca' ba'i phyag rgya gsum po ni ji ltar bca' /
NK009(ta)003:2107: gang bskyed pa'i lha gsum po ni gang bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:2108: byin gyis brlab pa la phyi nang gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2109: sngags gsum po 'dzab kyi grangs su bgrang ba dang brgyad do //
NK009(ta)003:2110: dang po byin gyis rlob byed gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:2111: g.yas dkar gyi bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pas g.yas su bsham /
NK009(ta)003:2112: g.yon dmar gyi rak+ta byin gyis brlab pas g.yon du bsham /
NK009(ta)003:2113: dbus mthing gi gtor ma byin gyis brlab pas dbus su bshams te go rim yang bstan to //
NK009(ta)003:2116: pho thod mo thod ma ning thod //
NK009(ta)003:2117: ba lim rak+ta bdud rtsi sbyar //
NK009(ta)003:2118: zhes pas ma ning thod par bdud rtsi bsham /
NK009(ta)003:2119: pho thod du gtor ma bsham /
NK009(ta)003:2120: mo thod du rak+ta bsham par bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:2121: gsum pa bshams pa'i dngos po gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:2122: gtsang phud la a mri ta sbyar ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:2123: 'bru sna la dpal zan rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2124: khrag sna tshogs tshad sha sna dang bcas pa bsham pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2125: bzhi pa sbyang ba gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:2127: ram yam kham gis bsregs sbyang bkrus //
NK009(ta)003:2129: ram las me 'bar nyes skyon bsregs //
NK009(ta)003:2130: yam las rlung byung thal ba gtor //
NK009(ta)003:2131: kham las chu byung sbyangs par bsgom mo //
NK009(ta)003:2133: 'bru gsum yi ge gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:2136: h'u mthing gas gtor ma brlab par yang bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:2137: lnga pa phyag rgya gsum la bdud rtsi la dung phor 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya bca' /
NK009(ta)003:2138: gtor ma la gzhong pa 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya bca' /
NK009(ta)003:2139: rak+ta la pad+ma 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya baca'o //
NK009(ta)003:2140: drug pa bskyed pa'i lha gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:2141: bdud rtsi'i lbu ba las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:2142: gtor ma'i lbu ba las khams gsum rnam rgyal bskyed raka ta'i lbu ba las rta mgrin bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:2143: bsrung yang srung la bya ba'ang byed do //
NK009(ta)003:2144: bdun pa byin gyis brlab pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:2147: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pa la gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2148: bdud rtsi phyi ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2149: nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2150: gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2152: bdud rtsi'i snod ma ning gi thod pa de mi dmigs pa las /
NK009(ta)003:2153: b+h+r+aum las thod pa'i gzhal yas khang rdo rje'i ra bas bskor bar bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2154: de'i nang bdud rtsi'i steng du zla ba /
NK009(ta)003:2155: de'i steng du a dkar po bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2156: de las 'od 'phros pas stong gsum gyi lha'i bdud rtsi dang /
NK009(ta)003:2159: sman dang bcud thams cad bkug ste a la thim /
NK009(ta)003:2160: 'dzab bzlas pa dang a zhu nas bdud rtsis khengs par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2161: de nas rdzas la bsang gtor bya /
NK009(ta)003:2164: khro bo'i gur du bsam pa ni phyi ltar brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2165: gnyis pa nang star brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2166: snod 'dra nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2167: shar du glang sha dri chen /
NK009(ta)003:2170: byang du khyi sha klad rgyas /
NK009(ta)003:2171: dbus su mi sha byang sems /
NK009(ta)003:2177: dbus su zhing bcu'i sems kyi dwangs ma dang /
NK009(ta)003:2178: h'u las 'od 'phros zhing bcu'i sha dang /
NK009(ta)003:2179: bdud rtsi bkug pa sogs kun la 'agre'o //
NK009(ta)003:2183: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK009(ta)003:2187: byang du rgya gram dril bu /
NK009(ta)003:2188: dbus su rdo rje dril bu'o //
NK009(ta)003:2189: de ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK009(ta)003:2200: des sku mdog phyag mtshan rgyan rnams rdzogs par bskyed pa ni sku yi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK009(ta)003:2202: thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od 'phros pas don gnyis byas /
NK009(ta)003:2203: tshur 'dus sku yab yum la thim /
NK009(ta)003:2204: de zhu bdud rtsi chen po'i ngo bor bsam pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2205: nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2207: gsum pa gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2210: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pas rta mgrin gsang ba'i yum bzhi dang bcas pa bskyed de /
NK009(ta)003:2211: yum bde ba rgyas byed mas mdun nas 'khril /
NK009(ta)003:2212: yum rmongs byed mas g.yon nas 'khril /
NK009(ta)003:2214: yum za byed mas rgyab nas 'khril /
NK009(ta)003:2215: de la dmigs te 'dzab bzlas pas /
NK009(ta)003:2216: dus gsum bud+d+ha'i thugs kyi bdud rtsi rta mgrin la thim /
NK009(ta)003:2217: des bskul sbyor ba byas pas bde ba ma bzod
NK009(ta)003:2218: bdud rtsir zhu ba rdo rjes dkrugs pas bdud rtsi
NK009(ta)003:2219: rgyas pa ni gsang ba ltar brlabs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2220: gnyis pa de tsam ma nus na bsdus pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2223: sems kyis bdud rtsir bsam mo //
NK009(ta)003:2224: bdud rtsi brlab pa tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:2225: gnyis pa gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:2228: ba lim phyi ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2229: ba lim nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2230: ba lim gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2232: gtor snod b+h+r+aum las thod pa'i gzhal yas khang rdo rje'i ra bas bskor bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2233: gtor ma'i steng du pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2234: steng du h'u las h'u dang n+ri gnyis bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2236: khams gsum gyi bla ma'i zhing bcu 'dul 'di bzla /
NK009(ta)003:2237: sku dgra bsgral ba'i phyir zhing bcu'i dam nyams n+ri la thim ste zhu /
NK009(ta)003:2241: d+h+au pe dkar mo spos chen mo //
NK009(ta)003:2242: push+pe sngon po me tog ma //
NK009(ta)003:2243: +aa lo ke dmar mo mar me ma //
NK009(ta)003:2244: gan+d+he ljang gu dri chab ma //
NK009(ta)003:2245: re re la'ang dpag tu med par 'phro ba ni phyi ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2246: gnyis pa nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2247: yang h'u las 'od 'phros zhing bcu'i lhu dum phung por bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2249: l+aa se dkar mo rdo rje 'gying //
NK009(ta)003:2250: m+aa le sngon mo rat+na phreng //
NK009(ta)003:2251: g+airti ljang gu gar ma la //
NK009(ta)003:2252: n+airti ljang gu gar ma la //
NK009(ta)003:2253: re re la yang grangs med 'phro ba ni nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2254: gsum pa gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2256: zhing bcu'i glo snying gi phung por bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2258: gzugs kyi lha mo me long dkar //
NK009(ta)003:2259: sgra yi lha mo pi wam sngo //
NK009(ta)003:2260: dri yi lha mo dung chos ser //
NK009(ta)003:2261: ro yi lha mo zhal zas ljang //
NK009(ta)003:2262: reg gi lha mo na bza' smug /
NK009(ta)003:2263: re re la'ang grangs med 'phro ba ni gsang ba ltar byiin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2264: gnyis pa de tsam ma nus na bsdus pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2265: lus kyi gzhong pa 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya bca' /
NK009(ta)003:2267: sems kyis gtor ma gzhi bdud rtsi chen po la spris ma du chags par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2268: gtor ma brlab pa tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:2269: gsum pa rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:2272: rak+ta phyi ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2273: rak+ta nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2274: rak+ta gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2275: dang po snod ni b+h+r+aum las thod pa'i gzhal yas
NK009(ta)003:2276: khang rdo rje'i ra bas bskor ba stong gsum tsam
NK009(ta)003:2277: mo // rak+ta'i steng du pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2279: zhing bcu'i khrag drangs te dzahl thim /
NK009(ta)003:2281: de zhu bas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen por bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2282: rak+ta phyar pas ro che chung mang po rnal mar
NK009(ta)003:2283: shad shad song bar bsam pa ni phyi ltar byin
NK009(ta)003:2284: gyis brlab pa'o // gnyis pa nang ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2285: yang dzahls 'od 'phros zhing bcu'i rtsa khrag drangs dzahl thim /
NK009(ta)003:2286: de zhu ba las rtsa khrag gi rgya mtshor bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2287: phyar bas rtsa rgyas thams cad rnal mar shad shad
NK009(ta)003:2288: song bar bsam pa ni nang ltar byin gyis brlab
NK009(ta)003:2289: pa'o // gsum pa gsang ba ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2290: de nas yum gyi pad+ma yab kyi rdo rjes bskul bas dzahls 'od 'phros /
NK009(ta)003:2293: de zhu bas snying khrag gi rgya mtshor bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2294: phyar bas glo mchin dang snying dang rtsa rnams rnal
NK009(ta)003:2295: mar shad shad song bar bsam pa ni gsang ba
NK009(ta)003:2300: lus kyis pad+ma 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya bca' /
NK009(ta)003:2302: sems kyis rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen po mi ro dang rta ro chol le ba bsgom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2304: brgyad pa sngags gsum 'dzab kyi ched du bskyal ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:2305: bdud rtsi la brgya rtsa brgyad dam nyer gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2308: gnyis pa dal rnam pa gsum dngos bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2309: dang po gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam pa gsum 'phro 'du bskyed pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2310: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2312: dang po gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam pa gsum
NK009(ta)003:2313: mdo gsum rtsa ba brgyad yan lag lnga bcu rtsa
NK009(ta)003:2314: bzhi'o // 'phro 'du bskyed pa la de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK009(ta)003:2315: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK009(ta)003:2317: de yang rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK009(ta)003:2318: de bzhin nyid dang kun tu snang //
NK009(ta)003:2319: rgyu yi ting 'dzin bsgom byas la //
NK009(ta)003:2321: rgyud gzhan na mang ste ma spros so //
NK009(ta)003:2322: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2323: don bskor gyi dbang du byas te bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2324: 'bru gnyer gyi dbang du byas te bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2325: nyams su blang ba bsgom pa'i dbang du byas nas bshad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2327: mtshan gzhi de bzhin nyid de la mtshan nyid mkhas
NK009(ta)003:2328: pa'i slob dpon gyi bzhed pas chos bco brgyad dang
NK009(ta)003:2329: ldan te / de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du mtshon pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2330: de la dang po slob dpon pad 'byung gi bzhed pas /
NK009(ta)003:2332: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2336: ming gi rnam grangs dang lnga /
NK009(ta)003:2337: ma bstan pa'i skyon dang drug /
NK009(ta)003:2338: bstan pa'i phan yon dang bdun no //
NK009(ta)003:2340: dper na 'gro ba rigs drug gi nang nas mi
NK009(ta)003:2341: ngos 'dzin na mgo nag rkang leb smra bzhin ldan
NK009(ta)003:2343: dpe de dang 'dra bar chos thams cad kyi nang nas spros bral stong nyid de /
NK009(ta)003:2344: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du ngos 'dzin no //
NK009(ta)003:2346: 'o na stong nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin byas pas chog mod /
NK009(ta)003:2347: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bya ba ci dgos zer na /
NK009(ta)003:2348: de ni ye gdod ma nas chos thams cad stong nyid spros bral du yod pa las /
NK009(ta)003:2349: sgrub pa po'i blo de bazhinanyida du rtogs pas na /
NK009(ta)003:2350: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin zer ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2351: gsum pa dbye ba ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2352: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rnam par mi rtog pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK009(ta)003:2353: sems can thams cad la rang chas su gnas pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK009(ta)003:2354: las dang po pas bsgom pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:2356: sangs rgyas sgam ste ma mdzad /
NK009(ta)003:2357: sems can sgrin te ma bcos pa'i chos nyid stong nyid de'o //
NK009(ta)003:2360: gla rtsi la dri rang chas su yod pa ltar /
NK009(ta)003:2361: sems can thams cad la sangs rgyas rang chas su
NK009(ta)003:2362: yod pa'i rtags su snying ga'i rtsa mdud la a
NK009(ta)003:2363: re yod do // gsum pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2364: blo spyi'i rnam pas stong pa'i don spyi la /
NK009(ta)003:2365: blos bsgom bya sgom byed du byas nas stong pa la blos bsgom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2367: stong pa des mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa 'joms pa'i las can no //
NK009(ta)003:2368: lnga pa ming gi rnam grangs ni mang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2369: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK009(ta)003:2374: skye med kyi ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:2375: drug pa ma bstan pa'i skyon ni /
NK009(ta)003:2376: chos thams cad la stong nyid kyi rtsis ma zin na /
NK009(ta)003:2377: sku mdog rang rgyud par bsgom na 'dod pa'i khams kyi lhar skye /
NK009(ta)003:2378: phyag mtshan rang rgyud par bsgom na bdud dang srin por skye /
NK009(ta)003:2379: mgo brnyan rang rgyud par bsgom na dur khrod kyi wa'am nags kyi srin bur skye /
NK009(ta)003:2380: sbyor ba rang rgyud par bsgom na mngal gyi srin bur skye /
NK009(ta)003:2381: sgrol ba rang rgyud par bsgom na sems can dmyal bar skye'o //
NK009(ta)003:2382: bdun pa bstan pa'i phan yod ni /
NK009(ta)003:2383: dper na chan la phab thebs na klum du 'gyur la /
NK009(ta)003:2384: ma thebs na mi 'gyur ba ltar /
NK009(ta)003:2385: chos thams cad la stong nyid kyi rtsis zin na /
NK009(ta)003:2387: mnan sreg 'phang gsum byas tshad ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur la /
NK009(ta)003:2388: des ma zin na mi 'gyur ro zhes gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2389: gnyis pa slob dpon bi ma la mi tra na re /
NK009(ta)003:2390: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la bdun yod de /
NK009(ta)003:2391: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs yul /
NK009(ta)003:2399: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid stong nyid du dmigs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2403: cir yang mi dmigs par bzhag go //
NK009(ta)003:2405: lam du mi dmigs pa snang ba dang stong pa
NK009(ta)003:2406: zung 'jug snang stong dbyer med lam du khyer ro
NK009(ta)003:2408: gang la ngos bzung med par rang grol ba goms rtags so //
NK009(ta)003:2409: lnga pa nyon mongs gang sbyang na /
NK009(ta)003:2410: nyon mongs dngos 'dzin sbyong ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2415: chos sku thob pa'o gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2416: gsum pa slob dpon bal po sh+ai la many+dzu'i zhal nas /
NK009(ta)003:2417: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:2418: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gang gi chos yin pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2419: sku gsum po las gang du gtogs pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2423: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di gzhi'i chos yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2424: gnyis pa ni chos kyi sku yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2425: gsum pa de ni nam mkha' dang rdo rje yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2426: rtags ni 'khor ba rang grol ba'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2427: gnyis pa 'bru gnyer gyi dbang du byas na /
NK009(ta)003:2428: slob dpon chen po pad 'byung ni //
NK009(ta)003:2429: rdo rje khros pas de bzhin nyid bstan te //
NK009(ta)003:2431: skye med don gyi rdo rje /
NK009(ta)003:2432: pha lam rdzas kyi rdo rje /
NK009(ta)003:2433: mtshan ma rtags kyi rdo rje gsum las /
NK009(ta)003:2434: 'di skye med don gyi rdo rje yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2435: ru bi ma la'i zhal nas /
NK009(ta)003:2436: rdo rje la chos gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)003:2437: mi 'gyur ba'i phyir na rdo rje /
NK009(ta)003:2438: phar 'joms pa'i don gyis na rdo rje /
NK009(ta)003:2439: tshur cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i don gyis na rdo rje zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:2440: de gsum skye med don gyi rdo rje la tshang gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2443: stong nyid spros bral la 'jug ste /
NK009(ta)003:2444: de de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la tshang gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2445: ru pad 'byung gi zhal nas khros pa la gsum ste gang khros /
NK009(ta)003:2447: tshul lam thabs ji ltar khros gsum yin gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2448: gang khros na skye med kyi don stong pa nyid de khros /
NK009(ta)003:2450: mtshan ma'i rtog pa la khros /
NK009(ta)003:2451: tshul lam thabs ji ltar khros na ngang ngam shugs kyis khros pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:2452: dper na nyi ma shar bas mun pa dwangs pa ltar /
NK009(ta)003:2453: stong nyid rtogs pas dngos 'dzin zhi ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2456: nyi ma shar bas ba mo ngang gis dwangs pa ltar /
NK009(ta)003:2457: stong nyid rtogs pas dngos 'dzin 'jig pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2459: gshis ngan pa dgra la khros pa lta bu min te /
NK009(ta)003:2460: dper na tsha reg dang grang reg lta bu mngon du gyur pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2461: stong nyid bsgom pas dngos 'dzin 'jig pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2462: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin stong pa nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)003:2463: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin nyams su blang ba'i dbang du byas na las dang po pa /
NK009(ta)003:2465: las smin pa ba dang gsum gyi dbang du byas te /
NK009(ta)003:2466: stong nyid la sgra spyi tsam dang /
NK009(ta)003:2468: don rang gi mtshan nyid gsum du nyams su blang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2470: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin kun tu snang ba ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2471: don bskor gyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2472: 'bru gnyer gyi dbang du byas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2473: nyams su blang ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2474: dang po mtshan gzhi kun tu snang ba'i ting nge
NK009(ta)003:2475: 'dzin de la mtshan nyid du ru gsum gyis bzhed
NK009(ta)003:2476: pa'i chos bco brgyad dang ldan pa de /
NK009(ta)003:2477: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin du mtshon /
NK009(ta)003:2478: de yang pad 'byung gi bzhed pas /
NK009(ta)003:2479: dang po kun tu snang ba'i ting 'dzin ngos bzung ba dang gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2483: ming gi rnam grangs dang lnga /
NK009(ta)003:2484: ma bstan pa'i skyon dang drug /
NK009(ta)003:2485: bstan pa'i phan yon dang bdun no //
NK009(ta)003:2487: chos thams cad kyi nang nas snying rje sgyu ma
NK009(ta)003:2488: tsam kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngos
NK009(ta)003:2490: 'o na snying rje'i ting nge 'dzin mi zer bar /
NK009(ta)003:2491: kun tu snang zhes pa ci zer na /
NK009(ta)003:2492: snying rje des gong 'og gnyis mtshams sbyar bas na kun tu snang zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:2493: gsum pa de la dbye na gsum /
NK009(ta)003:2494: bud+d+ha'i kun snang ni thugs rje chen po'o //
NK009(ta)003:2495: sems can gyi kun snang ni snying rje tsam po ste /
NK009(ta)003:2496: khra spyang la yang phyogs cha can yod pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2497: las dang po pa don spyi la blo spyis bsgom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2499: bud+d+ha thob par byed pa'i las can no //
NK009(ta)003:2504: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:2506: ma bstan na sangs rgyas sems can gnyis ris su yang chad pas /
NK009(ta)003:2507: 'khor ba lte chad du mar la ltung bas mtshams mi sbyor ro //
NK009(ta)003:2509: snying rjes gong 'og gi mtshams sbyar nas /
NK009(ta)003:2510: stong pa nyid snying rje'i ros gang bar 'gyur ba'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2511: gnyis pa ru bi ma la ni bdun te /
NK009(ta)003:2512: kun tu snang ba'i dmigs yul gcig /
NK009(ta)003:2517: sa lam gang bgrod tshul drug /
NK009(ta)003:2521: gnyis pa snying rje phyogs med du bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2522: gsum pa lam du byams pa snying rje khyer ro //
NK009(ta)003:2523: bzhi pa sems can thams cad pha mar 'char ro //
NK009(ta)003:2524: lnga pa nyon mongs zhe sdang sbyong ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2526: bdun pa 'bras bu longs sku thob pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2527: gsum pa ru bal po ni kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin 'di lam gyi chos yin la /
NK009(ta)003:2528: sku gsum las longs sku yin la /
NK009(ta)003:2529: dpe ni bu gcig pa'i ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:2530: rtags ni sems can la lus srog gtong ba'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2531: gnyis pa 'bru gnyer ni zhe sdang gcod ces pas so //
NK009(ta)003:2533: dper na tsha reg gang na yod pa na grang reg med /
NK009(ta)003:2534: grang reg gang na yod pa na tsha reg med /
NK009(ta)003:2535: dpe de ltar gang zag gcig ni rgyud la zhe sdang skyes tsa na snying rje med /
NK009(ta)003:2536: snying rje skyes tsa na zhe sdang med pas /
NK009(ta)003:2537: lhan cig mi gnas pa'i 'gal ba ste /
NK009(ta)003:2538: kun tu snang ba'i snying rjes zhe sdang bcad pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2541: byams pa bsgom pas snying rjes rjes su 'gro zhing /
NK009(ta)003:2543: ru bal po sgra rtag 'dzin sgro 'dogs dang /
NK009(ta)003:2544: sgra min pa'i nges shes ltar skad cig lhan cig mi gnas 'gal te /
NK009(ta)003:2545: snying rjes zhe sdang gcod gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2546: gsum pa nyams su blang ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:2547: gong gi stong nyid kyi ngang las snying rje rang
NK009(ta)003:2548: shugs su skye bas sems can la dmigs pa'i snying
NK009(ta)003:2549: rje bsgoms te / kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:2550: gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2551: dang po don bskor gyi dbang du byas na mtshan
NK009(ta)003:2552: gzhi rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin de la mtshan nyid bco
NK009(ta)003:2553: brgyad dang ldan pas de rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin mtshon
NK009(ta)003:2554: pa'o // de yang ru pad+ma ni /
NK009(ta)003:2555: dang po chos thams cad kyi nang nas h'u sngon
NK009(ta)003:2556: po yig 'bru'i rnam pa ste rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK009(ta)003:2558: 'o na yig 'bru'i ting nge 'dzin bya mod /
NK009(ta)003:2559: rgyu zhes ci bya zer na /
NK009(ta)003:2560: de ni h'u rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK009(ta)003:2561: brten pa lha thams cad de las bskyed pa'i rgyur 'dug pas so //
NK009(ta)003:2563: bud+d+ha'i thugs ni h'u de la ye shes lnga dang ldan pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2564: sems can thams cad kyi rtsa mdud la h'u rang chas su gnas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2565: las dang po pa h'u blos bsgom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2567: rten dang brten pa skyed par byed pa'i las can no //
NK009(ta)003:2569: rgyu'i sa bon gyi yig 'bru skyed byed kyi ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:2570: drug pa ma bstan na bskyed pa'i rim pa cho
NK009(ta)003:2571: ga dang mi ldan zhing rdzogs par mi 'gyur ro
NK009(ta)003:2572: // bdun pa bstan pas cho ga rdzogs par 'gyur pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2574: dang po dmigs yul yig 'bru la dmigs /
NK009(ta)003:2575: sgom thabs 'bur du gtod pa ltar bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2580: 'bras bu sprul sku thob gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2586: rtags gsal snang ngo gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:2588: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yis //
NK009(ta)003:2589: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thigs pa shar //
NK009(ta)003:2592: mtshon chen zhes pa ni kha dog la'ang 'gro /
NK009(ta)003:2593: r+ts+wa yi lo ma la yang 'gro /
NK009(ta)003:2595: pho mo'i mtshan ma la'ang 'gro mod kyi /
NK009(ta)003:2597: brten pa lha h'u 'dis mtshon pa la bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2598: mtshon chen ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2599: sngon po ni h'u gi kha dog go //
NK009(ta)003:2600: 'bar ba ni h'u de las yig 'bru mang po 'phros shig 'dus pas so //
NK009(ta)003:2602: bud+d+ha'i dgongs pa sems kyi mtshon te /
NK009(ta)003:2603: mi 'gyur bas sngon po mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar bas so gsungs //
NK009(ta)003:2605: rten dang brten par bcas pa'i rgyur mtshon pa'i h'u sngon po 'od zer 'bar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2607: nam mkha' la snang ba nam mkha' /
NK009(ta)003:2610: chos nyid kyi nam mkha' bzhi las chos nyid kyi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2613: don 'dril ba'i phyir na thigs pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2614: don thog tu phebs pa'i phyir na thigs pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:2616: h'u de la ye shes lnga ldan pas 'dril lo //
NK009(ta)003:2618: rten dang brten pa'i thog tu phebs pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2620: chos kyi dbyings nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu las thugs rje thigs pa ltar shar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2623: mtshon chen sngon po longs sku /
NK009(ta)003:2624: thigs pa sprul skur bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:2625: gsum pa nyams su len na /
NK009(ta)003:2626: h'u gser dngul la lugs su blugs pa 'dra ba zhig bsgom mo //
NK009(ta)003:2628: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2629: srog gi sgo ru shar ba dang //
NK009(ta)003:2630: snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK009(ta)003:2633: srog ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h'u yin la /
NK009(ta)003:2634: sgor shar ba la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:2635: 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:2636: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:2637: de la dang po 'byung ba rim brtsegs la gsum sde /
NK009(ta)003:2640: gsang ba'i 'byung ba rim brtsegs so //
NK009(ta)003:2641: dang po phyi'i 'byung ba la mdo lnga /
NK009(ta)003:2643: yan lag sum cu tham pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2644: dang po mdo lnga 'byung ba lnga'o //
NK009(ta)003:2645: rtsa ba drug ni phyi 'byung ba dang ji ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2646: nang phung po dang gang ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2647: gsang ba nyon mongs pa dang ji ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2648: gsal ba lha dang gang ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2649: bde ba ye shes dang ji ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2650: stong pa chos dang gang ltar sbyar /
NK009(ta)003:2652: de yang srog ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi h'u de nyid do //
NK009(ta)003:2653: h'u de s+pha ra na phata /
NK009(ta)003:2655: sam ha ra na h'u byas te tshur bsdus pas
NK009(ta)003:2656: h'u de nus pa dang ldan par song ba ni
NK009(ta)003:2658: h'u de las e gcig chad /
NK009(ta)003:2661: e sam ha ra na h'u /
NK009(ta)003:2662: tshur bsdus pas e las nam mkha' gru gsum tshad med pa zhig bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2663: phyi 'byung ba nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgor shar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2665: bar du nyon mongs pa gti mug /
NK009(ta)003:2669: de thams cad chos nyid stong par 'dus pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2670: de nas h'u las yam chad /
NK009(ta)003:2672: sam ha ra na h'u kun la 'gre /
NK009(ta)003:2673: phar spro tshur 'dus pa las rlung rdo rje rgya gram sngo skya bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2674: phyi 'byung ba rlung gi dal sgor shar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2675: nang lus kyi skyod byed do //
NK009(ta)003:2677: lha don grub dang sgrol ma /
NK009(ta)003:2679: de thams cad chos dbyings stong par 'dus so //
NK009(ta)003:2680: yang h'u las ra zhig chad /
NK009(ta)003:2682: tshur 'dus pas ra las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2686: lha snang mtha' dang m+aa ma k+ai /
NK009(ta)003:2688: de thams cad chos nyid stong par 'dus so //
NK009(ta)003:2689: yang h'u las sum gcig chad /
NK009(ta)003:2690: phar spros tshur 'dus pa las dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi sra zhing 'thas pa'i steng du /
NK009(ta)003:2691: yang h'u las kem gcig chad /
NK009(ta)003:2692: phar spros tshur 'dus keng rus kyi ri rab sngo mkhregs su 'dug pa /
NK009(ta)003:2693: dpag tshad brgyad khri yar thon pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2694: de ni 'byung ba sa'i sgor shar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:2695: nang rus pa nyon mongs zhe sdang /
NK009(ta)003:2696: lha rdo rje sems dpa' dang sangs rgyas spyan /
NK009(ta)003:2697: ye shes me long ye shes /
NK009(ta)003:2698: de thams cad chos nyid stong par 'dus so //
NK009(ta)003:2699: yang h'u las ram gcig chad /
NK009(ta)003:2701: ri rab steng du me gru gsum du 'bar bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:2707: de thams cad chos nyid stong par 'dus so //
NK009(ta)003:2708: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa'i sgor shar ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:2710: phar spros tshur 'dus pa las b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi
NK009(ta)003:2711: shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum zhes pas yeshesa
NK009(ta)003:2712: kyi gzhal yas khang gru bzhi pa /
NK009(ta)003:2714: phyi rin po che sna lnga las grub pa /
NK009(ta)003:2715: nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK009(ta)003:2716: de yang thod pa skam po'i 'gram sha ra ri can gyi bar /
NK009(ta)003:2717: rlon pa lcang lo can kha bad du btang ba /
NK009(ta)003:2718: thod pa de rnams kyi kha nas me 'bar ba /
NK009(ta)003:2720: mig nas gdung ba'i mchi ma khrag tu skyugs pa /
NK009(ta)003:2721: gnam lcags ur mos gzer btab pa /
NK009(ta)003:2722: rgyu ma'i zung gis sbrel bas brtsegs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2726: keng rus kyi ri rab khrag dang rnag gi tshom bur 'khyil ba /
NK009(ta)003:2727: dri chen gyi zhal zas zhal zhal 'dra ste steng dri chu'i chag chag btab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2728: steng gi phub ni lha brgyad kyi ka ba /
NK009(ta)003:2731: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dral bu /
NK009(ta)003:2740: mi'u rigs bzhi srid pa spyi blugs su bshus pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK009(ta)003:2743: dregs pa chen po bsgral ba'i tsit+ta'i tog /
NK009(ta)003:2744: de'i phyi na dur khrod chen po brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK009(ta)003:2745: de'i phyi na dur khrod kyi chas bzhi la /
NK009(ta)003:2746: shar na bya kang+ka skad sgrog pa /
NK009(ta)003:2747: lho na khyi kyi ling du zug pa /
NK009(ta)003:2750: dbus kyi pho brang 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dam /
NK009(ta)003:2751: rgya mdud 'degs pa gang 'os su bsgom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2753: gong gi h'u las dzahmh'u bam hoh lha mo bzhi 'phros pas /
NK009(ta)003:2754: dbus kyi pho brang 'khor lo'i mthil du pam las pad+ma /
NK009(ta)003:2757: ti ra bam zhes brjod pas ru dra pho kha sbub /
NK009(ta)003:2760: de'i steng du mos pa'i gdan la rang gi dgra bgegs gding ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2762: dzahmh'u bam hoh shar dang shar lho rnams su brgya byin dang me lha nas /
NK009(ta)003:2763: 'og phyogs sa bdag gi bar bkug la pho kha sbub /
NK009(ta)003:2764: mo gan rkyal du byin pa 'khril ba 'gyel bar rings so //
NK009(ta)003:2768: byang gnod sbyin bkug la gding ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2769: lha snam la phur srung dgod de /
NK009(ta)003:2772: yam las rlung gi da la sngo //
NK009(ta)003:2773: ram las me dkyil gru gsum dmar //
NK009(ta)003:2774: bam las chu dkyil dkar po zlum //
NK009(ta)003:2775: sum las sa gzhi gru bzhi ser //
NK009(ta)003:2776: kem las keng rus ri rab 'bar //
NK009(ta)003:2777: de steng b+h+r+aum las grub pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:2778: mdzes pa'i gzhal yas thod pa'i mkhar //
NK009(ta)003:2779: mchog phran dral phyam nyi zla'i mig /
NK009(ta)003:2781: ces bshad pa'i don yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2782: de rnams phyi bskyed pa'i rim pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2783: gnyis pa nang bskyed pa'i rim pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2784: rang gi lus la tshang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2786: rkang pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor te //
NK009(ta)003:2788: bsus pa chu yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK009(ta)003:2789: pho ba sa yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK009(ta)003:2790: brang ni keng rus ri rab yin //
NK009(ta)003:2791: mgo bo klad pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK009(ta)003:2792: rtsa gnas dbus na lha tshogs bzhugs //
NK009(ta)003:2793: zhes pas dkyil 'khor lus la tshang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2794: lus 'dom gang gru bzhi ni dkyil 'khor gru bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:2795: 'khor lo lnga po dbus kyi pho brang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:2800: so dang sen mo tog dang /
NK009(ta)003:2801: rdo rje rin po che'i rgyal mtshan /
NK009(ta)003:2804: rtsa rgyus rin chen pha gu /
NK009(ta)003:2805: rus pa'i tshigs d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa phyed /
NK009(ta)003:2808: skra dang ba spu me ri'o //
NK009(ta)003:2809: khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ltar rtsa gnas la phur bu'i lha tshogs tshang ba 'god do //
NK009(ta)003:2811: gsum pa gsang ba bskyed pa'i rim pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:2812: rang gi sems la lha dang dkyil 'khor thams cad tshang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2814: sems la mtha' dbus med pas nam mkha' stong pa /
NK009(ta)003:2815: sems yang zhing g.yeng bas rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)003:2816: sems rlan zhing mnyen pas chu'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)003:2817: sems sra zhing mi 'gyur bas sa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)003:2818: sems rgya che dpangs mtho ste ri rab /
NK009(ta)003:2819: sems gsal zhing rno bas me'i dkyil 'khor /
NK009(ta)003:2820: sems la thams cad 'dus pas gzhal yas khang /
NK009(ta)003:2821: kun gzhi'i rnam shes lte ba /
NK009(ta)003:2823: sgo lnga'i rnam shes sgo bzhi /
NK009(ta)003:2825: rang sems rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)003:2826: sems la sna tshogs skye bas 'khor gyi lha tshogs yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2828: gsang ba bskyed pa'i rim pa tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:2831: gzhal yas rnam par dag pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:2832: yang dag nyid du ngas bshad bya //
NK009(ta)003:2833: rdo rje'i gur du byung ba ni //
NK009(ta)003:2834: phyi yi bgegs kyis mi tshugs rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2835: bka' yi 'khor los brgyan pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:2836: nang gi bdud kyis mi tshugs rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2837: chos 'byung nang du gsal ba ni //
NK009(ta)003:2838: chos kyi dbyings las byung ba'i rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2839: 'byung ba bzhi yis bskyed pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:2840: yum bzhi'i mkha' la gnas pa'i rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2841: gzhal yas gru bzhi 'byung ba ni //
NK009(ta)003:2842: sangs rgyas sems can mnyam pa'i rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2843: sgo bzhi par yang byung ba ni //
NK009(ta)003:2844: dran pa nye bar bzhi yi rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2845: sgo ba bzhi ni stobs lnga'o //
NK009(ta)003:2846: rta babs bzhi ru byung ba ni //
NK009(ta)003:2847: yang dag spong ba bzhi yi rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2848: chos kyi 'khor lo bzhi po ni //
NK009(ta)003:2849: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi yi rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2850: 'dod yon lnga yi lha mo ni //
NK009(ta)003:2851: dbang po lnga po gsos 'debs rtags //
NK009(ta)003:2852: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa ba phyed pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:2853: byang chub yan lag bdun du bshad //
NK009(ta)003:2854: ka ba brgyad kyis brgyan pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:2855: 'phags lam yan lag brgyad du bshad //
NK009(ta)003:2856: pany+tsa re kh+aa ye shes lnga //
NK009(ta)003:2857: gru gsum rnam thar gsum yin te //
NK009(ta)003:2858: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams rdzogs //
NK009(ta)003:2860: thod mkhar gyi rnam dag ni /
NK009(ta)003:2861: thod pa skam po'i 'gram chos sku /
NK009(ta)003:2862: sha ra ri can longs sku /
NK009(ta)003:2864: kha nas me 'bar rnam rtog sreg /
NK009(ta)003:2865: sna nas du ba 'thul ba byin brlabs //
NK009(ta)003:2866: mig nas mchi ma thugs rje che ba /
NK009(ta)003:2867: gnam lcags ur mo'i gzer skye med ston pa /
NK009(ta)003:2868: rgyu ma'i zung thabs shes rgya ma chad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2869: 'og gzhi la m+aam sa'i sa gzhi gti mug dag /
NK009(ta)003:2872: rnag khrag tshom bur 'khyil sprul sku /
NK009(ta)003:2873: dri chu chag chag longs sku /
NK009(ta)003:2875: steng gi phub la lha brgyad ka ba steng lha'i lo ka dbang du sdud pa /
NK009(ta)003:2876: klu brgyad gdung ma 'og klu brgyad dbang du sdud pa /
NK009(ta)003:2877: gza' dang rgyu skar sa bla dbang du sdud pa /
NK009(ta)003:2878: mi'i g.yang gzhi'i bar mi'i lo ka dbang du sdud pa /
NK009(ta)003:2881: nyi zla thabs shes rgyas thebs pa /
NK009(ta)003:2882: phyi'i dur khrod brgyad tshogs brgyad dag /
NK009(ta)003:2883: shar na bya skad mi rtag pa ston pa /
NK009(ta)003:2884: lho na khyi zug pas 'khor ba 'dul /
NK009(ta)003:2885: nub na me 'bar ba byin rlabs che /
NK009(ta)003:2886: byang du du ba 'thul ba 'khor ba ma spangs par sangs rgya'o //
NK009(ta)003:2887: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:2888: spyi don gsum pa lhar bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:2889: chos kyi sku'i ngo bo bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal bskyed pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2890: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i ngo bo phyogs bcu'i khro bo'i dal bskyed pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2891: sprul pa'i sku'i ngo bo phur pa rdzas kyi dal bskyed pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2892: dang po chos kyi sku'i ngo bo bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:2893: bskyed pa dngos dang gsal gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:2898: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal bskyed pa'i rgyu sems dpa' bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2899: bskyed pa'i sku'i cha lugs bzhi bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2900: bskyed pa'i khyad par mtshan nyid bzhi po gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2901: bskyed pa'i gnas skabs bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2902: bskyed thabs kyi cho ga bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2903: bskyed pa'i lha bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2904: bskyed pa'i lha yi sbyang gzhi bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2905: bskyed pa'i lha yi nges tshig bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2906: bskyed pa la rnam dbye bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2907: bskyed pa la lam khyer bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:2909: dang po bskyed pa'i rgyu'i sems dpa' bzhi po ni /
NK009(ta)003:2910: sngon dus mtshams la 'jug tsa na /
NK009(ta)003:2911: rang yi dam lhar mos pa byas pa de dam tshig gi sems dpa' yin /
NK009(ta)003:2912: de nas ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom nas cho ga
NK009(ta)003:2913: gsum gyis bskyed pa ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' yin
NK009(ta)003:2914: / de nas rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' spyan 'dren pa de lha ye shes sems dpa' yin /
NK009(ta)003:2915: de gnyis su med pas bsres pa de gnyis su med pa'i ye shes sems dpa' yin /
NK009(ta)003:2916: bskyed rim cig mi bsgom na mi bsgom zhes bya /
NK009(ta)003:2918: de bzhi ma tshang ba mi srid pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2919: gnyis pa bskyed pa'i cha lugs bzhi la phyogs gcig tu a thang chad pa med de /
NK009(ta)003:2920: rgyud kyi rjes su 'brangs nas phur pa gsang rgyud le'u bcu gnyis pa na /
NK009(ta)003:2921: rdo rje gzhon nu dbu stong phyag stong spyan bye ba stong mnga' bar bshad /
NK009(ta)003:2922: phur pa myang 'das le'u bzhi par ru dra btul
NK009(ta)003:2923: tsa na rdo rje gzhon nu dbu dgu phyag bco
NK009(ta)003:2924: brgyad par bshad / rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa
NK009(ta)003:2925: sogs na rdo rje gzhon nu dbu gsum phyag drug
NK009(ta)003:2926: brgyad par bshad / par gshad / k+ai la ya
NK009(ta)003:2927: tan+t+ra bcu gnyis 'byung ba'i rgyun la sogs pa nas
NK009(ta)003:2928: brgyad par bshad / par gshad / // rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gcig phyag gnyis par bshad pas /
NK009(ta)003:2930: gshin rje gshed la sogs thams cad na de ltar sna tshogs su bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:2931: gsum pa bskyed pa'i khyad par mtshan nyid bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:2932: khro bo byas pas bdud dang srin po khros pa lta bu min te /
NK009(ta)003:2933: thugs rje chen pos gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs su bstan pa yin pas /
NK009(ta)003:2934: blo yang rab byams pa dang snying rjes lha bsgom pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2935: blo rab cig gis dag pa'i lha bsgom pa yin /
NK009(ta)003:2936: blo 'bring gis rnam pa tsam du lha bsgom pa yin /
NK009(ta)003:2937: blo tha mas lha yi nga rgyal tsam du lha bsgom pa yin /
NK009(ta)003:2938: sngags pa lha lam pa bya ba nga rgyal tsam gyis kyang 'grub pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2939: bzhi pa bskyed pa'i gnas skabs bzhi la las dang po pas shes pa lhar bskyed pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2940: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:2942: las goms pa pas bdag nyid lhar bsgom pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2943: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK009(ta)003:2945: las smin pa pas phung po lhar bsgom pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2946: phung po rdo rjer gtams byas nas /
NK009(ta)003:2948: las mthar phyin pas yul thams cad lhar bsgom pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:2949: srid pa rdo rje phur bu'i lha //
NK009(ta)003:2951: lnga pa bskyed thabs kyi cho ga bzhi la /
NK009(ta)003:2952: blo yang rab gcig gis skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed do //
NK009(ta)003:2953: rnam rtog gzhan gyis bar ma chod pas bzang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2954: ye shes kyi tshogs pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2955: blo rab cig stong pa dang snying rje'i ngang nas rtsa sngags brjod pas lhar langs te /
NK009(ta)003:2956: rtog pa nyung bas bsod nams dang ye shes gnyis ka yod do //
NK009(ta)003:2957: blo 'bring zhig chos gsum gyi lhar ldang ste /
NK009(ta)003:2960: sku yongs su rdzogs pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:2963: de gyur pas rdo rje gzhon nu bskyed pa'o /
NK009(ta)003:2964: blo tha ma zhig gis bskyed rgyu'i chos gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:2965: bskyed thabs kyi chos bcu drug gis bskyed de /
NK009(ta)003:2966: de yang bskyed rgyu ni gsung yig 'bru //
NK009(ta)003:2968: rgyu rdo rje 'chang dkar po gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:2970: dang po rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h+aum mthing nag de
NK009(ta)003:2971: gtso bo'i gdan thog tu babs te de las 'od
NK009(ta)003:2972: zer 'phro ba / mdzad pa bsdu ba bsdus te
NK009(ta)003:2973: brtan par 'khod pa bzhi byas pas rdo rje rtse
NK009(ta)003:2974: zer 'phro ba / dgu par song / de las kyang 'od zer spro ba /
NK009(ta)003:2977: bsdus te brtan par 'khod pa bzhi /
NK009(ta)003:2978: rdo rje de rgyu'i rdo rje 'chang dkar por song /
NK009(ta)003:2979: de las kyang 'od zer spro ba /
NK009(ta)003:2982: bsdus te brtan par 'khod pa las rtsa sngags brjod /
NK009(ta)003:2983: rdo rje gzhon nu sku che la yan lag rags par bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:2984: de las kyang 'od zer spro ba /
NK009(ta)003:2987: bsdus te brtan par 'khod pa bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:2988: bcu drug gis bskyed pa'i rim pa yan lag dang ldan pa rdzogs pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:2989: drug pa bskyed pa'i lha bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:2990: gtso bo yab yum rdzogs pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:2993: sku gsung thugs kyi lha dang gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:2996: dang po srog gi lha ni /
NK009(ta)003:2997: bdag nyid kyi snying ga'i nang tsit+ta rin po che'i
NK009(ta)003:2998: pho brang du ye shes sems dpa' rdzus skyes rang
NK009(ta)003:3000: de'i snying gar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor sran ma'i gwa'u tsam /
NK009(ta)003:3001: de'i steng du rdo rje nas tsam /
NK009(ta)003:3002: de'i lte ba la rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h+aum spus bris pa tsam /
NK009(ta)003:3003: de'i mtha' ma ni k+ai la ya 'bru dgus bskor bar ba sgom /
NK009(ta)003:3004: de'i sgo srung du rta mgrin gsang ba'i yum bzhi dang bcas pa bsgom ste lha bdun no //
NK009(ta)003:3005: gnyis pa sku gsung thugs kyi lha ni /
NK009(ta)003:3007: spyi bor bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum dkar po bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:3008: mgrin par pad+ma he ru ka yab yum dmar po bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:3009: thugs kar badz+ra he ru ka yab yum mthing ga /
NK009(ta)003:3010: lte bar rat+na he ru ka yab yum ser po /
NK009(ta)003:3011: gsang bar karma he ru ka yab yum ljang gur bsgom mo /
NK009(ta)003:3012: gsum pa rgyan gyi lha ni /
NK009(ta)003:3013: dbang bskur ba'i dus dbang rtags su rigs lnga cha gcig dbu la bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK009(ta)003:3014: des na sku gsung thugs kyi yab yum bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3015: dbu rgyan la bcu ste nyi shu /
NK009(ta)003:3016: srog gi lha bdun te nyer bdun no //
NK009(ta)003:3017: bzhi pa go cha'i lha ni /
NK009(ta)003:3018: ba spu'i bu ga re nas rdzus skyes su khro chung re re ste khrab gyon pa ltar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3021: sku gsung kyi lha sgong skyes /
NK009(ta)003:3022: ye shes sems dpa' rdzus skyes /
NK009(ta)003:3023: byang sems zhu ba las byung ba dbu rgyan lha mngal skyes /
NK009(ta)003:3024: go cha'i lha drod gsher las skyes pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3025: dal gyi lha la sbyar na /
NK009(ta)003:3027: phyogs bcu'i khro bo mngal skyes /
NK009(ta)003:3028: mgo brnyan nyi shu sgong skyes /
NK009(ta)003:3029: dam can srung ma drod gsher las skyes te /
NK009(ta)003:3030: sbyang gzhi sems can gyi skye gnas bzhi sbyong ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3031: brgyad pa bskyed pa'i nges tshig bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:3041: 'khor gyi lha thams cad 'byung bas rtsa ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3043: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum dal srog gi lha /
NK009(ta)003:3046: go cha'i lha rnams 'khor yin pas bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:3047: dgu pa bskyed pa'i rnam dbye bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:3048: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal gyi bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3049: de ni ye shes sems dpa' yin no //
NK009(ta)003:3050: bdag rtsa ba'i dal gyi phyogs bcu'i khro bo'i dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3051: de ni sku gsung thugs kyi lha'o //
NK009(ta)003:3052: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal gyi phur pa rdzas kyi dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3053: de ni phyag tha ma'i phur pa rnams so //
NK009(ta)003:3054: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal gyi phur srung bcu gnyis yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3055: de ni ba spu'i khro chung rnams so //
NK009(ta)003:3056: bcu pa bskyed pa'i lam khyer bzhi ni /
NK009(ta)003:3057: rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK009(ta)003:3058: rang sems gzhi yi rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)003:3059: sa bon kun khyab til mar 'dra //
NK009(ta)003:3060: rtogs na sangs rgyas ngo mtshar che //
NK009(ta)003:3061: bgrod pa lam gyi rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)003:3062: thabs shes sku gsum ye shes lnga //
NK009(ta)003:3063: chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bya //
NK009(ta)003:3064: rtogs pa 'bras bu'i rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK009(ta)003:3065: sku lnga ye shes dgu ldan te //
NK009(ta)003:3067: gzhi lam 'bras bu rtogs gyur na //
NK009(ta)003:3068: chos sku spros bral mngon du 'gyur //
NK009(ta)003:3069: zhes pas gzhi lam 'bras gsum po de chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin /
NK009(ta)003:3070: de la brten nas rnam dag bstan pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3071: yab yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba bstan pa ni dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3072: sku mdog mthing nag chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3073: dbu gsum sku gsum rnam thar gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:3074: phyag drug phar phyin drug go //
NK009(ta)003:3075: zhabs bzhi rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3076: dang po rdo rje rtse dgu theg pa dgu /
NK009(ta)003:3079: kha t+w+aam rtse gsum dug gsum gcod /
NK009(ta)003:3080: ri rab phur bu gdug pa 'dul ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3081: dur khrod kyi chas dgu la byug pa'i rdzas gsum /
NK009(ta)003:3084: dang po thal chen gyi tshom bu chos sku /
NK009(ta)003:3086: zhag gi zo ris sprul sku'o //
NK009(ta)003:3087: gnyis pa glang chen ko rlon theg chen /
NK009(ta)003:3088: zhing chen mtha' gnyis spangs pa /
NK009(ta)003:3089: stag sham phrin las rdzogs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3090: gsum pa sbrul chun zhe sdang 'joms /
NK009(ta)003:3099: 'jigs su rung ba gsum sku yi /
NK009(ta)003:3105: zhi ba thugs kyi gar gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:3107: chad pa ma yin rig cing gsal //
NK009(ta)003:3108: rtag pa ma yin ngos bzung med //
NK009(ta)003:3109: snang stong dbyer med gtan la dbab //
NK009(ta)003:3110: mi bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du bsgom //
NK009(ta)003:3112: bskyed rdzogs dbyer med du bsgom mo //
NK009(ta)003:3113: de ltar bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa gnyis la sbyar na yan lag brgyad cu'o //
NK009(ta)003:3114: gnyis pa gsal gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3116: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)003:3118: dam tshig ngo bo nges tshig dbye ba sbyar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3121: snying rjes dug gsum bsgral lo gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3123: snying rjes zhes khams gsum sems can /
NK009(ta)003:3124: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu dang gnyis su med nas bsgral ba yin no gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3126: snying rje rgyun mi chad pa'i byang chub sems //
NK009(ta)003:3127: bsgral med ngang du rtogs na dam tshig yin //
NK009(ta)003:3130: snying rjes kun nas bslangs te gdug can bsgral ba dam tshig gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3131: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK009(ta)003:3133: zhe sdang gis bsad cing phrag dog gis mnan pa ma yin te /
NK009(ta)003:3134: thugs rjes sems can 'khor ba las bsgral bar bya gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3136: ye shes kyis nyon mongs zil gyis mnan te /
NK009(ta)003:3137: byang sems skye shi med pa de la bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3139: sems nyid skye shi med pa de la bsad rgyu med la /
NK009(ta)003:3140: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes su mnan /
NK009(ta)003:3141: mi 'gyur ba la mnan rgyu med gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3142: phung po rdo rjer gtams byas nas //
NK009(ta)003:3143: zhes pad 'byung gis gzugs phung la sogs lnga rdo rje phung po'i rigs lngar gtams pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3146: phung po rnam par shes pa'i phung po ste /
NK009(ta)003:3147: rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed la /
NK009(ta)003:3148: ba spu'i bu ga khro chung gis gtams pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3150: gzas pa po gnas spor tsa na /
NK009(ta)003:3151: lha dang gnyis su med par gtams pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3152: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK009(ta)003:3154: pad 'byung tshogs brgyad sems dpa' sems mar bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:3155: rdo rje gzhon nu las khro bo khro mor 'byung bas so gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3157: rnam par shes pas lha yi nga rgyal la bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3158: ru bal po phung po lha skur bsgom pa bya'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3159: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:3161: ru gsum gyi dgongs pa bsdu ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3162: rgyud kyi dgongs pa gsum bshad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3168: k+ai li lha dang k+ai la ya phur pa gso ba /
NK009(ta)003:3171: bam h'u dbang du bsdu ba /
NK009(ta)003:3177: k+ai la ya skye med 'gag med /
NK009(ta)003:3178: sarba nyon mongs ye shes su sgyur cig big+h+n+aana ye shes kyis nyon mongs thams cad gzir cig /
NK009(ta)003:3181: phata nyon mongs sregs shig pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3184: badz+ra k+ai li rdo rje phur bu /
NK009(ta)003:3187: big+h+n+aana phur pa'i ri rab kyis mnan pa /
NK009(ta)003:3191: gnyis pa rgyud kyi dgongs pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:3192: lha dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK009(ta)003:3193: chos nyid dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK009(ta)003:3194: byang sems dgongs pa dang sbyar ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3196: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags h'u ngo //
NK009(ta)003:3198: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya'o //
NK009(ta)003:3199: bskul ba las kyi sngags ni /
NK009(ta)003:3201: bzlas pa las kyi sngags ni /
NK009(ta)003:3203: gnyis pa chos nyid dang sbyar na /
NK009(ta)003:3205: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:3206: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK009(ta)003:3207: gsal la ngos gzung med pa /
NK009(ta)003:3208: sgra grags stong du bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3210: rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku /
NK009(ta)003:3211: badz+ra dbyings gting mtha' med pa /
NK009(ta)003:3213: phur bu las 'od zer 'phroos pas bsgral /
NK009(ta)003:3217: h'u bud+d+ha'i thugs ye shes lnga /
NK009(ta)003:3218: phata khro bo khro mo 'phro ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3219: gsum pa thams cad 'dus lugs ni /
NK009(ta)003:3220: rdo rje phur ba khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)003:3221: ni dpal chen yab yin te //
NK009(ta)003:3222: badz+ra shes rab yum yin no //
NK009(ta)003:3223: k+ai ni ye shes khro bo la //
NK009(ta)003:3224: li ni dbyings kyi khro mo bcu //
NK009(ta)003:3225: k+ai ni thabs kyi mche ba can //
NK009(ta)003:3226: la ni shes rab gshog pa can //
NK009(ta)003:3227: ya ni sras mchog phur pa ste //
NK009(ta)003:3228: h'u ni phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK009(ta)003:3230: big+ha ni dgra dang sgrib pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3231: n+aan ni dgra dang bgegs mnan no //
NK009(ta)003:3232: bam ni dbang du sdud pa ste //
NK009(ta)003:3233: h'u ni brlag par byed pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3234: phata kyis sgrol ba'i phrin las rdzogs //
NK009(ta)003:3236: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3237: gnyis pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i ngo bo phyogs bcu'i khro bo bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3241: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK009(ta)003:3244: gnyis pa bskyed pa dngos ni gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:3247: yan lag bzhi brgya dang bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3249: byang sems rgyu'i khro bo bcu bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3250: bskyed pa ye shes kyi khro bo bcu bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3251: gdul bya sprul pa'i khro bo bcu bya ba yod na gang ltar yin /
NK009(ta)003:3252: drag po 'dul ba gsung gi khro bo bcu bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3253: ye shes rtse gcig thugs kyi khro bo bcu bya ba yod na ji ltar yin /
NK009(ta)003:3254: grangs nges pa dang ma nges pa bcu bya ba yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3255: 'khor nges pa dang ma nges pa bcu zhes bya ba yod na gang la zer /
NK009(ta)003:3256: sku mdog nges pa dang ma nges pa bcu po gang la zer /
NK009(ta)003:3257: phyag mtshan nges pa dang ma nges pa bcu po ji ltar yin /
NK009(ta)003:3258: rnam dag nges pa dang ma nges pa bcu po ci yin /
NK009(ta)003:3260: de las dang po byang sems rgyu'i khro bo bcu zer kyang /
NK009(ta)003:3261: de re re la bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi yod do //
NK009(ta)003:3262: gang zhe na khro bo bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3264: mgo brnyan pha bcu ma bcu ste bzhi bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3265: sgo ma bzhi ste zhe bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3266: de ltar bcu po la so sor brtsis pas bzhi brgya dang bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi yod /
NK009(ta)003:3267: de las dang po rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags /
NK009(ta)003:3268: sa bon bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi las bskyed dgos te /
NK009(ta)003:3269: de'i sngon du gtso bo yab yum la mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3270: yab kyi mkha' mi dmigs pa las /
NK009(ta)003:3271: a tsan+d+ra man+da la zhes pas zla ba'i steng du h'u las rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK009(ta)003:3273: bu ga phata kyis bkag go //
NK009(ta)003:3274: yum gyi mkha' mi dmigs pa las /
NK009(ta)003:3275: a s+aur+ya man+da la bam zhes pas nyi ma'i steng
NK009(ta)003:3276: du pam las pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa ze'u 'bru
NK009(ta)003:3277: la a'o // de nas snyoms 'jug byas te /
NK009(ta)003:3278: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK009(ta)003:3280: r+aa ga ya mi zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:3281: sngar gyi phyogs skyong bcu byi chings su bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK009(ta)003:3282: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i sbyor mtshams nas h'u sbrel ma bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3283: thig le dkar dmar bcu ste bzhi bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3284: dzahmh'u bam hohbazhi ste zhe bzhi de rnams rang rang gi phyogs ma nor bar spro'o //
NK009(ta)003:3285: ngag tu'ang h'u h'u zhes brjod do //
NK009(ta)003:3286: gnyis pa bskyed pa ye shes kyi khro bo bcu ni /
NK009(ta)003:3287: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags bcu brjod pas lha krong krong bskyed pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3288: de'ang tshangs pa bsnol ba'i gdan la h'u gnyis thig le gnyis bzhi po las /
NK009(ta)003:3289: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK009(ta)003:3290: h'u gcig las khro bo h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3291: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa ri d+ai pa ya ti h'u
NK009(ta)003:3292: zhes barjooda pas h'u gcig las yum rdo rje sgra
NK009(ta)003:3293: 'byin ma bskyed / badz+ra su ka ra mu kha h'u /
NK009(ta)003:3294: badz+ra u ka mu ka ye h'u /
NK009(ta)003:3295: zhes brjod pas thig le gcig las phag gi mgo can g.yas su bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3296: badz+ra badz+ra i shu pa mu khi h'u /
NK009(ta)003:3297: u ga si mu khi ho /
NK009(ta)003:3298: zhes brjod pas rmig pa'i mgo can g.yon du bskyed do //
NK009(ta)003:3299: gdan thog re rer lha bzhi bzhi bskyed pa ni tshad med pa bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3300: de ni rgyud kyi rjes su 'brangs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3301: man ngag gi rjes su 'brang na /
NK009(ta)003:3302: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra zhes brjod pas khro bo h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3303: h'u zhes pas yum rdo rje sgra 'byin ma bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3304: gardza zhes pas phag mgo can dang gardza h'u zhes pas smig bu'i mgo can bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3305: de ltar 'og gi stobs bo che'i bar du bskyed do //
NK009(ta)003:3306: de nas bi da ya bing bing h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:3307: ces pa shar sgor lcags kyu ma bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3308: de nas dril bu ma'i bar du 'agre'o //
NK009(ta)003:3309: gsum pa gdul bya sprul pa sku'i khro bo bcu ni /
NK009(ta)003:3312: de nas khro bo rnams zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK009(ta)003:3314: mgo brnyan zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK009(ta)003:3315: bsnyen dus su sku mdog sna tshogs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3316: bzhi pa drag po 'dul ba gsung gi khro bo bcu ni /
NK009(ta)003:3317: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra zhes pa nas ma h+aa ba la'i bar dang /
NK009(ta)003:3318: bzlas pa sngags ha na ha na'i bar dang /
NK009(ta)003:3319: pa tsa pa tsa zhes pa'i bar thog 'dril ba ltar bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3320: lnga pa ye shes rtse gcig thugs kyi khro bo bcu ni /
NK009(ta)003:3321: khro bcu'i phur pa sor bcu gnyis pa /
NK009(ta)003:3322: mgo brnyan gyi phur pa sor brgyad pa /
NK009(ta)003:3323: sgo ma'i phur pa sor bzhi pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:3324: lha phur lnga bcu rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3328: drug pa grangs nges pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3329: 'o na khro bcu kho nar grangs nges pa ci yod /
NK009(ta)003:3330: yang na bco lnga nyi shu /
NK009(ta)003:3331: yang na lnga drug gis chog mod zer na /
NK009(ta)003:3332: de'i lan ni bcu kho nar nges te /
NK009(ta)003:3333: gdul bya phyogs skyong bcu 'dul bas so //
NK009(ta)003:3334: mang ba dang nyung ba don med do //
NK009(ta)003:3335: 'o na steng gi khro bo h'u ka ra dang /
NK009(ta)003:3336: 'og gi stobs po che gnyis go sa spos na ci lto zer na /
NK009(ta)003:3338: h'u ka ra ni lha dang tshangs pa'i gnyen po yin la /
NK009(ta)003:3339: stobs po che sa bdag gi gnyen po yin pas spos na gdul bya mi thul lo //
NK009(ta)003:3341: bdun pa 'khor nges ma nges ni /
NK009(ta)003:3342: steng gi h'u ka ra'i 'khor phag rmig bu 'di 'og gi stobs po che la spos /
NK009(ta)003:3343: dred dang byi ba h'u ka ra la spos na 'gal lam mi 'gal zer na /
NK009(ta)003:3345: tshangs pa'i 'khor na zla ba phag mgo can dang /
NK009(ta)003:3346: nyi ma rmig bu'i mgo can yod pas de 'dul /
NK009(ta)003:3347: 'og sa bdag pho nya dred dang byi bas ba'i mgo can yod /
NK009(ta)003:3350: yab kyi mche ba can rnams yum la spos la /
NK009(ta)003:3351: yum gyi gshog pa can yab la spos na mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK009(ta)003:3353: mche ba can dang yab rnams chos mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3354: gshog pa can dang yum rnams chos mthun pas so //
NK009(ta)003:3355: de ji ltar mthun na phag la gtsang rme med pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3356: h'u ka ra la rnam rtog med pas chos mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3357: rmig bu skam la gnas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3358: sgra 'byin thar pa la gnas pa chos mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3359: yang stag ri mo bkra ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3360: rnam rgyal chos spyan bkra ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3361: bya rgod srog sdom pa dang yum snyems ma rnam rtog sdom pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3363: dbyug sngon khro la 'gyings pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3364: bya rog cho gsum rig pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3365: sder mo dus gsum mkhyen pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3366: sha ba rdzi rno ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3367: gshin rje shes rab rno ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3368: 'ug pas mun pa la mthong ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3369: dur khod kyis gdul bya la mthong ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3370: gzig la theg le yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3371: mi g.yo ba chos thams cad thig le gcig tu sdud pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3372: khwa ta la sgrib shing yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3373: yum gyi chos nyid mi mthong ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3374: byi la'i skad kyis byi ba brgyal ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3375: rta mgrin gyi skad kyis klu brgyal ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3376: pu shud mig rtsi yod pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3377: yum la thugs rje yod pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3378: spyang ki gsod la dga' ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3379: khro bo gdug pa sgrol ba la dga' ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3380: khras byi chung za ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3381: yum dam nyams za ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3382: seng ges ri dwags zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3383: bdud rtsi 'khyil bas dam nyams zil gyis gnon pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3384: pha wam mtha' gnyis spong ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3385: yum mtha' gnyis spong ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3387: khro bo dam nyams la gtum pa mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3388: sre mo yang rtsal che ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3389: yum rtogs tshad che ba mthun /
NK009(ta)003:3390: dred bu la snying rje che ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3391: khro bo sems can la snying rje che ba mthun //
