NK009(ta)003:3392: byi ba sgo mang yang phug gcig tu sdod pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3393: yum chen chos can mang yang chos nyid gcig tu
NK009(ta)003:3394: sdod pa mthun pas spor mi btub bo zhes rgyud
NK009(ta)003:3395: las gsungs so // brgyad pa sku mdog nges ma nges ni /
NK009(ta)003:3400: mtshams rnams phyogs gnyis kyi 'od 'dus pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3401: steng nam mkha'i mdog 'og mun pa'i mdog /
NK009(ta)003:3402: zhal g.yas g.yon kyang mtshams ltar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3403: zhal lhar du mgo brnyan 'gyur bar gsang rgyud nas bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:3404: sgrub dus su thams cad mthing nag 'ba' zhig ste /
NK009(ta)003:3406: zhal re la ni phyag gnyis pa //
NK009(ta)003:3407: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK009(ta)003:3408: kun kyang rdo rje phur pa 'dril //
NK009(ta)003:3410: skabs kha cig tu yum rang rkyang bar shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:3411: dgu pa phyag mtshan nges ma nges ni /
NK009(ta)003:3412: khro bo rnams dang po gnyis rdo rjes b+han dmar dkrugs pa /
NK009(ta)003:3413: bar pa gnyis rang rang gi gdan phyogs skyong gi phyag mtshan 'phrogs pa /
NK009(ta)003:3414: tha ma ri rab phur pa 'dril ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3417: sgrub dus su lha thams cad de ltar bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:3420: ngag 'khyal rdzun dang srog gcod log lta phra //
NK009(ta)003:3421: ma byin len dang tshig rtsub gnod sems dang //
NK009(ta)003:3422: brnab sems 'dod log dang ni de bcu'i yul rnams ni //
NK009(ta)003:3423: rnam par dag pa khro bo khro mor shar //
NK009(ta)003:3424: yum rnams ye shes shes rab tshul khrims bsam gtan thabs //
NK009(ta)003:3425: brtson 'grus sbyin smon stobs dang bzod pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3426: h'u ka ra 'dod pa'i skyon spangs shing skye ba la mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3427: rnam rgyal ma byin len spangs yo byad la mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3428: dbyug sngon can log lta spangs nas ye shes la mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3429: gshin rje gshed srog gcod spangs nas tshe la mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3430: stobs po che'i bar du shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:3431: rdo rje sgra 'byin ma ni ye shes pha rol phyin ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:3432: rdo rje snyems ma shes rab pha rol phyin ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:3433: rdo rje sder mo tshul khrims pha rol phyin ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:3434: dur khrod bdag mo bsam gtan pha rol phyin ma ste /
NK009(ta)003:3435: bskyod byed ma'i bar du shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:3436: phra men phag mgo can gnyid dbyings su dag pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3437: rmig bu'i mgo can gnyid kyi mtshan nyid dbyings su dag pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3438: stag mgo can sems kyi dngos po dag pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3439: bya rgod mgo can sems kyi sems yul rnam par dag pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3440: g.yag mgo can mun pa dag pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3441: bya rog mgo can mun yul dag ces bya ba'i bar du sbyar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3442: shar sgor pu shud mgo can byams pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3443: lho sgor skya ga'i mgo can snying rje'o //
NK009(ta)003:3444: nub sgor srin bya'i mgo can dga' ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3445: byang sgor khra yi mgo can btang snyoms so //
NK009(ta)003:3446: rgyas par gsang rgyud du blta'o //
NK009(ta)003:3453: h'u 'og ma yum rdo rje sgra 'byin /
NK009(ta)003:3455: gardza 'og ma rmig bu'i mgo can /
NK009(ta)003:3460: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra bskyed sngags /
NK009(ta)003:3462: bzlas pa las kyi sngags yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3469: h'u ka ra bskyed kyang des bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3470: byin gyis brlabs kyang des rlob /
NK009(ta)003:3473: ru pad 'byung h'u ka ra la bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:3474: rang skal gyi phrin las gang 'dul na spyir phyogs skyong bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3476: gnyis pa rtog pa gang dag na /
NK009(ta)003:3479: gsum pa rnam dag la spyir dbang bcu /
NK009(ta)003:3480: sgos skye ba la dbang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:3484: chas dgu dang ldan pas khro bo /
NK009(ta)003:3487: mgo lus mi gcig pas phra men no gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3489: 'byung khungs las dang yon tan 'bras bzhir 'dod /
NK009(ta)003:3490: h'u ka ra rol stobs las byung /
NK009(ta)003:3493: 'bras bu mos pa la dbang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:3495: 'byung khungs par bcu las ye shes so //
NK009(ta)003:3497: yon tan ma rig pa sel /
NK009(ta)003:3499: sprul pa'i phra men la gang gis sprul /
NK009(ta)003:3501: sprul pa rang gi ngo bo /
NK009(ta)003:3502: sprul nas ci mdzad dang bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3503: dang po spyir khro bcu yab yum las /
NK009(ta)003:3504: khyad par h'u ka ra yab yum las /
NK009(ta)003:3505: gnyis pa smon lam ye shes las so //
NK009(ta)003:3507: mdzad pa phyogs skyong bcu'i bu dang bu mo 'dul /
NK009(ta)003:3509: dpe'i phra men gser dngul bsres pa phra men yol go zer /
NK009(ta)003:3510: don dbyings ye shes 'dres pa la phra men zer /
NK009(ta)003:3511: rtags mgo lus mi gcig pas so //
NK009(ta)003:3512: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK009(ta)003:3514: thugs ye shes kyi rdo rje gzhon nu la gnyis /
NK009(ta)003:3515: don gyi gzhon nu la 'pho 'gyur med /
NK009(ta)003:3516: rtags kyi gzhon nu mtshan dpe can no gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3518: rdo rje yang dag pa'i ye shes de rtogs na bgres kud med pas gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)003:3520: rdo rje stong pa de mi 'gyur bas gzhon nu /
NK009(ta)003:3521: rdo rje'i rigs rdo rje rigs kyis 'dzin /
NK009(ta)003:3524: spyir rig rigs lnga'i ngo bo mthong ba la rig pa 'dzin pa zer /
NK009(ta)003:3530: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK009(ta)003:3532: rnam par smin dang tshe la dbang //
NK009(ta)003:3533: phyag rgya che dang lhun gyis grub //
NK009(ta)003:3535: de re re la brgyad de /
NK009(ta)003:3543: dang po rnam smin gyi rgyu lha'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3544: gnyis pa dus ni bskyed rdzogs la brtan pa thob dus so //
NK009(ta)003:3545: gsum pa grub thob kyi cha lugs so //
NK009(ta)003:3546: bzhi pa lha'i dal la dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3548: drug pa mos pas spyod pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3549: bdun pa chos rmi lam du nyan no //
NK009(ta)003:3550: brgyad pa 'gro don dngos su byed do //
NK009(ta)003:3551: gnyis pa tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi rgyu ni rnam smin man chad do //
NK009(ta)003:3552: gnyis pa dus ni rnam smin mthar phyin tsa na'o //
NK009(ta)003:3553: gsum pa sprul pa sku'i cha lugs so //
NK009(ta)003:3554: bzhi pa stong gsum dal du dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3556: drug pa lus mdor ba la sangs rgyas sa la 'gro /
NK009(ta)003:3557: bdun pa chos sgra nyan tsam du thos /
NK009(ta)003:3558: brgyad pa 'gro don dgongs pas byed do //
NK009(ta)003:3559: gsum pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi rgyu ni tshe dbang man chad do //
NK009(ta)003:3560: gnyis pa dus tshe dbang mthar phyin tsa na'o //
NK009(ta)003:3561: gsum pa cha lugs longs sku'o //
NK009(ta)003:3562: bzhi pa dgongs pa nam mkha' tsam /
NK009(ta)003:3564: drug pa sa brgyad man chad /
NK009(ta)003:3565: bdun pa chos longs sku nyan no //
NK009(ta)003:3566: brgyad pa 'gro don dgongs pas khyab tshad do //
NK009(ta)003:3567: bzhi pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rgyu ni phyag rgya man chad do //
NK009(ta)003:3568: gnyis pa dus mthar phyin tsa na'o //
NK009(ta)003:3569: gsum pa cha lugs bud+d+ha dngos /
NK009(ta)003:3570: bzhi pa chos dbyings la dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3572: drug pa sa bcu rgyun mtha' man chad /
NK009(ta)003:3573: bdun pa chos chos sku la nyan /
NK009(ta)003:3574: brgyad pa 'gro don nam mkha' khyab tshad la'o //
NK009(ta)003:3575: srid pa rdo rje sgrub mdzod cig /
NK009(ta)003:3578: srid pa rigs drug la bya /
NK009(ta)003:3579: de sku de'i lhar 'grub par mdzod cig par ro gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3581: srid pa khams gsum la khyab /
NK009(ta)003:3582: khams gsum sku re re'i sku gsung thugs su 'grub par mdzod gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3585: de'ang mi srid pa'i srid pa lha la mi mi srid /
NK009(ta)003:3586: ci'ang srid pa'i srid pa mi la skyid sdug srid /
NK009(ta)003:3587: srid la mi srid pa'i srid pa dmyal ba la bde ba mi srid pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3588: yang na srid pa 'greng bu 'phred nyal kha sbubs so //
NK009(ta)003:3589: de gsum chos skur rtogs par bya gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3590: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)003:3593: srid pa byang chub sems yin te //
NK009(ta)003:3594: de ka rdo rje de ka phur pa'i lha //
NK009(ta)003:3598: de nyid phur pa'i lhar shes dgos gsungs //
NK009(ta)003:3600: spyir srid pa gsum lha yin phan chad sku re'i lhar shes par bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3601: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK009(ta)003:3602: ces pas sgrub pa zung ste /
NK009(ta)003:3603: thun mong gi sgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3605: dang po la gsum phyi ltar sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3608: dang po la steng sgo'i man ngag /
NK009(ta)003:3611: sbyor yab yum ltar du sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3612: sgrol yab yum ltar du sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3613: tshe yab yum ltar du sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3614: dngos grub yab yum ltar du sgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3619: phyi rig sngags gtsug tor ltar du sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3620: nang ltar gsang sngags gos sngon ltar du sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:3621: gsang ba gzungs sngags rnam 'joms ltar du sgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3622: rtsa ba ma mo ltar sgrub na /
NK009(ta)003:3629: gnyis pa ma mo ltar sgrub pa la /
NK009(ta)003:3632: rtsa ba 'jig rten par sgrub na /
NK009(ta)003:3639: ru pad+ma ni ye shes la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3640: rtogs pa'i ye shes gnas lugs /
NK009(ta)003:3641: spros pa'i ye shes 'gro don te /
NK009(ta)003:3642: rdo rje gzhon nur sgrub par bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3643: ru bi ma la ye shes 'dra /
NK009(ta)003:3644: khro bo la bcas bcos gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3645: khro bo ye shes chen po dang bcas pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3646: snying rje chen po sngon du song nas khro bor bcos pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3647: de ni sku zhi yang 'bar ba'i cha lugs can no //
NK009(ta)003:3650: shugs kyis khro ba gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3651: ye shes chos skur yod pa de chos skur sgrub pa'o zhes gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3652: longs sku khro bcu'i dal tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:3653: gsum pa sprul sku'i ngo bo phur pa sras kyi dal la gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3657: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK009(ta)003:3658: zhes pa sh+lo ka gcig go //
NK009(ta)003:3664: sku gsum gyi klong nas bskyed pa la chos gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3665: sku gsung thugs ye shes rtse gcig tu byin brlab pa la yig 'bru gsum dgos na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3666: chu srin rnam grol gyi phyag rgyas blangs pa la dgos pa gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3667: rigs lnga'i dbang bskur ba la rdzas gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3668: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlob pa la sngags gsum dgos na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3669: gu gul gyis bdug pa la nus pa gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3670: yungs kar gyis brab pa la sngags rdzas ting nge 'dzin gsum dgos na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3671: rak+ta byugs pa la ngar gsum bskyed na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3672: sras mchog gi rnam dbye mu bzhi yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3673: phur pa'i rnam dbye la chos bdun yod na gang yin zhes pa dang bcu'o //
NK009(ta)003:3674: dang po sras mchog 'di yang stong 'khor los sgyur
NK009(ta)003:3675: ba'i rgyal po'i sras mchog dang chos mthun par sbyar
NK009(ta)003:3676: dgos te / dper na stong 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i sras de /
NK009(ta)003:3678: ma'i rgyud nyid dag par skye dgos pa dang 'dra
NK009(ta)003:3679: bar sras mchog 'di yang sku gsum gyi klong nas
NK009(ta)003:3680: bskyed de / de yang dang po sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa nas stong par bsgom pa ni chos sku'o //
NK009(ta)003:3681: de'i ngang nas yab yum mkha' gsang nas h'u gcig chad /
NK009(ta)003:3683: badz+ra k+ai li brjod pas sku stod khro bo zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK009(ta)003:3684: sku smad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum pa dmar lhang nge ba bskyed pa ni sprul sku'o //
NK009(ta)003:3686: 'dir ni dbu gsum phyag drug dang //
NK009(ta)003:3687: zhal gcig phyag kyang bzhi pa ste //
NK009(ta)003:3688: de las mang ba ngas ma bshad //
NK009(ta)003:3691: lte ba man chad sku smad ni //
NK009(ta)003:3692: sngo sangs mi bzad 'jigs pa'i tshul //
NK009(ta)003:3694: grangs ni sras mchog rab brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK009(ta)003:3697: yang tha badz+ra 'dus pa gcig tu 'dus pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3698: de ltar rgyal po de skye ba bzang yang 'khor
NK009(ta)003:3699: dang longs spyod med na rgyal por mi tshud pa
NK009(ta)003:3700: dang 'dra bar / 'dir yang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK009(ta)003:3701: skur byin gyis ma brlabs na sku gsum mi tshang
NK009(ta)003:3702: dang 'dra bar / ste / phur pa'i gcum gzhogs
NK009(ta)003:3703: kyi dbus ldir ba der b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang
NK009(ta)003:3704: dang 'dra bar / ste / du bskyed la / der gtso bo yab yum bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:3706: gcum gzhogs brgyad la phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo yab yum mgo brnyan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3707: rgya mdud gong ma'i nang du h'u ka ra yab yum khyung mgo ltar rong nger bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3708: rgya mdud 'og ma'i nang du stobs po che yab yum gyad gdung 'degs tshul du bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3709: logs bzhir sgo ma bzhi bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3710: dbal gyi gnyar phur srung bcu gnyis bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:3711: rgya mdud gong ma'i logs 'dir rigs lnga rdo rje gzhon nu'i dbu rgyan du bskyed de /
NK009(ta)003:3713: sku bzhi ngang las da la thams cad rdzogs //
NK009(ta)003:3714: logs brgyad rang bzhin khro bo brgyad //
NK009(ta)003:3715: zur brgyad 'byung ba'i khro mo brgyad //
NK009(ta)003:3716: steng 'og lha yi rang bzhin no //
NK009(ta)003:3718: gnyis pa ye shes rtse gcig tu brlab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3719: de ltar rgyal po 'khor longs spyod ldan yang /
NK009(ta)003:3720: rgyal po sku gzi brjid chung na rgyal por mi tshud pas /
NK009(ta)003:3721: sras mchog 'di yang sku gsung thugs ye shes rtse gcig tu byin gyis brlabs te /
NK009(ta)003:3722: dbal gyi zur gsum du h'u gsum /
NK009(ta)003:3724: rtse mo la a dkar po zhig bsam ste /
NK009(ta)003:3726: logs la phata gsum bzhag pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3727: zur gsum h'u gsum bzhag pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3730: sa ma ya dzah chu srin rnam grol gyi phyag rgyas blangs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3731: chu srin gyis 'dzin shes gtong mi shes pa ltar /
NK009(ta)003:3732: sras mchog gis kyang gang la btab pa mi btang ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:3735: de dus sor mo rgyab tu bsnol //
NK009(ta)003:3736: gung mo gnyis po rab tu bsgreng //
NK009(ta)003:3737: de yi bar du phur ba gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:3738: de nas sor mo pad 'drar bya /
NK009(ta)003:3739: kha ma bye ba'i tshul du ni //
NK009(ta)003:3740: lag mthil bar du phur ba 'dril //
NK009(ta)003:3742: bzhi pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:3743: de ltar rgyal po gzi brjid dang ldan yang /
NK009(ta)003:3744: rgyal po'i spyi bor dbang ma bskur na /
NK009(ta)003:3746: 'dir yang rigs lngas dbang bskur te /
NK009(ta)003:3747: g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la ma las nyi ma'i steng du rigs lnga /
NK009(ta)003:3748: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la a las zla ba'i
NK009(ta)003:3749: dal steng du yum lnga yab yum sbyor ba mdzad
NK009(ta)003:3750: / byang sems sras mchog la thim pas dbang bskur ro //
NK009(ta)003:3752: lag g.yas mthil du nyi dkyil la //
NK009(ta)003:3753: kun bzang 'od dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK009(ta)003:3754: g.yon gyi a las zla dkyil du //
NK009(ta)003:3755: kun tu bzang mo a las bskyed //
NK009(ta)003:3756: gung mo rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK009(ta)003:3757: mthe bong la ni mi bskyod pa //
NK009(ta)003:3758: mdzub mo rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK009(ta)003:3759: srin lag don yod grub pa ste //
NK009(ta)003:3760: mathe'u chung snang ba mtha' yas so //
NK009(ta)003:3761: g.yon pa lnga la yum lnga'o //
NK009(ta)003:3762: thabs dang shes rab snyoms 'jug dus //
NK009(ta)003:3763: sor mo cung zad bsnol bar bya //
NK009(ta)003:3764: phur pa 'dril bar bya ba yin //
NK009(ta)003:3766: lnga pa sku gsung thugs byin gyis yum lnga /
NK009(ta)003:3768: de ltar rgyal po la dbang bskur kyang bsod nams
NK009(ta)003:3769: tshad med pa dang mi ldan na rgyal por mi
NK009(ta)003:3770: tshud pas 'dir sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa
NK009(ta)003:3771: ni / sras mchog gi spyi bor 'khor lo la bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3772: de las bud+d+ha k+ai li'i sngags kyis bskor bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3773: de brjod pas bud+d+ha'i sku'i dngos grub thams cad 'dus te /
NK009(ta)003:3774: skus khams gsum dus gcig tu sgrol nus par byin gyis brlabs so //
NK009(ta)003:3776: +aahpad+ma k+ai li k+ai la yas bskor /
NK009(ta)003:3778: gsung gis khams gsum dus gcig tu sgrol nus par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3779: thugs kar rdo rje sngon po'i lte ba la h'u bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3780: de la h'u badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la yas bskor ba la /
NK009(ta)003:3781: de barjooda pas bud+d+ha'i thugs kyi dngos grub 'dus /
NK009(ta)003:3782: thugs kyis khams gsum dus gcig tu sgrol nus par byin gyi brlabs so //
NK009(ta)003:3783: drug pa yungs kar gyis brab pa la /
NK009(ta)003:3784: sngags rdzas ting nge 'dzin gsum las /
NK009(ta)003:3785: dper na rgyal po dmag la 'gro na go cha gyon dgos pa ltar /
NK009(ta)003:3786: 'dir yang be ta la'i sngags brjod cing /
NK009(ta)003:3787: yungs kar nag gis brab pas lus khrab chung gis go mtshams med par song bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3789: khros pa'i rgyal po bskul ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:3790: yungs nag byin rlabs khro chung bskyed //
NK009(ta)003:3792: bdun pa gu gul gyis bdug pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3793: sngags rdzas ting nge 'dzin ni gsum las /
NK009(ta)003:3794: rgyal po dmag la 'gro na go gyon kyang mi phan te /
NK009(ta)003:3795: mtshon rnon po dgos pa dang 'dra bar /
NK009(ta)003:3796: 'dir yang ma gu ta la'i sngags brjod cing /
NK009(ta)003:3797: gu gul gyis bdug pas gdug pa'i dbal dang ldan pas /
NK009(ta)003:3798: mi bzad pa'i ngar thogs rdugs med pa'i nus pa dang ldan par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3800: phur pa ngar rnams bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:3801: lce log nag po'i dud pas bdug /
NK009(ta)003:3803: brgyad pa rak+tasa byug pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3804: sngags rdzas ting nge 'dzin gsum las /
NK009(ta)003:3805: rgyal po des mtshon rnon po dgra la thebs dgos pa 'dra bar /
NK009(ta)003:3806: ra tri ta'i sngags brjod cing /
NK009(ta)003:3807: rak+tasa byugs pas phur pa dmar nag dud kha reg par 'joms pa zhig tu bsam /
NK009(ta)003:3809: gdug pa brlag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:3810: ra khyi phag pa'i khrag gis byug /
NK009(ta)003:3812: de nas rgyal po phas kyi g.yul las rgyal te /
NK009(ta)003:3813: dgra bo'i yul thob dgos pa dang 'dra bar /
NK009(ta)003:3814: sa ma ya tish+tha lhan zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:3815: dgra bgegs kyi snying dkar nag mtshams su bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK009(ta)003:3817: gnad chen thams cad 'dus pa yi //
NK009(ta)003:3818: dkar nag mtshams su gdab par bya //
NK009(ta)003:3820: dgu pa sras mchog gi rnam dbye ni bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:3821: sras ma yin kyang mchog yin pa'i mu dang /
NK009(ta)003:3822: sras kyang yin la mchog kyang yin pa'i mu dang /
NK009(ta)003:3823: sras yin la mchog ma yin pa'i mu dang /
NK009(ta)003:3824: sras ma yin la mchog ma yin pa'i mu dang bzhi'o //
NK009(ta)003:3826: phur pa rdzas kyi dal gyi bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3827: phur pa rdzas kyi dal gyi phyogs bcu khro bo'i dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3828: phur pa rdzas kyi dal gyi phur pa rdzas kyii dal cig yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3829: phur pa rdzas kyi dal gyi srung ma dam can rnam gsum yod na gang yin /
NK009(ta)003:3831: phur pa'i rgya mdud gong 'og gcum gzhogs dang bcas pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3832: gzhal yas khang mdzod dang 'dra ba yin la /
NK009(ta)003:3833: de'i nang du lha tshogs rdzas dang 'dra bar bskyed pa'i phyir na phur pa rdzas zhes bya la /
NK009(ta)003:3834: dal gyi ni lha tshogs tshang ma bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)003:3835: bcu pa phur pa'i rnam dbye ni gnyis te /
NK009(ta)003:3836: spyir gang zag rnam bzhi mthar phyin pa'i phur bu'i rgyud bzhi'i dbye ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:3837: bye brag tu mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3839: nam mkha' lta bu'i gang zag gi rig pa ye
NK009(ta)003:3840: shes kyi phur pa yul chos nyid kyi dbyings la
NK009(ta)003:3841: gdab pa dang / ri bo lta bu'i gang zag
NK009(ta)003:3842: gis thugs rje sprul pa'i phur pa yul khams gsum
NK009(ta)003:3843: sems can la gdab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3844: bya ka lan+ta ka lta bu'i gang zag gis gsang
NK009(ta)003:3845: ba byang chub sems kyi phur pa yum gyi mkha'
NK009(ta)003:3847: tsan+dana lta bu'i gang zag gis mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa yul dgra dang bgegs la gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3848: de re re la lnga lnga ste /
NK009(ta)003:3855: rig pa ye shes phur pa de //
NK009(ta)003:3856: gzung 'dzin med pa'i ngang du gdab //
NK009(ta)003:3857: lhang gis rtogs na thebs pa'i tshad /
NK009(ta)003:3858: 'bras bu chos sku skye med thob //
NK009(ta)003:3860: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa de //
NK009(ta)003:3861: 'gro la byams dang snying rjes gdab //
NK009(ta)003:3862: bdag gzhan gnyis med rtogs na thebs //
NK009(ta)003:3863: 'bras bu longs spyod rdzogs sku thob //
NK009(ta)003:3864: ma thebs ru dra srin por gol //
NK009(ta)003:3865: lhag pa byang sems phur pa de //
NK009(ta)003:3866: yum gyi mkha' klong dag par gdab //
NK009(ta)003:3867: bde ba dngos med thebs pa'i tshad //
NK009(ta)003:3868: 'bras bu sku gsum dbyer med thob //
NK009(ta)003:3870: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa de //
NK009(ta)003:3871: zhi drag dbang rgyas phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3873: gnyis pa mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa bye brag tu bshad pa la drug ste /
NK009(ta)003:3879: phur pa'i las dang drug go //
NK009(ta)003:3882: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)003:3883: zhi ba chos kyi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)003:3884: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)003:3885: yon tan rgyas pa'i phur bu'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)003:3886: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams ni //
NK009(ta)003:3887: gsung mchog dbang gi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)003:3888: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnasama ni //
NK009(ta)003:3889: drag po'i las kyi phur pa'i rgyu //
NK009(ta)003:3893: phur ni skye ba med pa'i dbyings //
NK009(ta)003:3894: pa ni 'gags pa med pa'i don //
NK009(ta)003:3895: phur ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK009(ta)003:3896: pa ni rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK009(ta)003:3897: gnyis su med pa'i mya ngan 'das //
NK009(ta)003:3898: sems kyi sems nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3899: chos kyi chos nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3900: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid phur pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3901: gsal bar bsgom na bskyed pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3902: gnyis su med na sbyor ba yin //
NK009(ta)003:3903: lhang gis rtogs na thebs pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3904: nyams 'og chud na bsgral ba yin //
NK009(ta)003:3908: sor bzhi 'byung ba bzhi yi tshad //
NK009(ta)003:3909: sor brgyad rnam shes brgyad kyi tshad //
NK009(ta)003:3910: bcu gnyis skye mched bcu gnyis tshad //
NK009(ta)003:3911: bco brgyad tshad du bstan pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:3912: khams ni bco brgyad 'joms pa'i tshad //
NK009(ta)003:3913: nas gang tshang du bstan pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:3914: byang chub sems mchog tshad du bstan //
NK009(ta)003:3917: don dam pa'i phur pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:3921: phur pa'i don ni rig pa'i ye shes te //
NK009(ta)003:3922: de yi yul ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK009(ta)003:3925: lcags sna dang shing sna lnga yi phur pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3927: sa lcags gnam lcags khro chu dang //
NK009(ta)003:3928: mi rta bsad pa'i mtshon rtse dang //
NK009(ta)003:3929: phal pa'i lcags dang lnga la bya //
NK009(ta)003:3933: rgya mdud gong ma chos sku ste //
NK009(ta)003:3934: gnyis pa longs spyod rdzogs pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:3935: rtse mo sprul pa'i sku yin pas //
NK009(ta)003:3936: mgo dang rtsa ba ma nor bar //
NK009(ta)003:3937: zur gsum pa ru rnam par gzhog /
NK009(ta)003:3941: tsan+dana dkar po'i phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:3942: nad rnams ma lus zhi bar byed //
NK009(ta)003:3943: skyer pa'i phur pa zur bzhi yis //
NK009(ta)003:3944: tshe dang longs spyod rgyas par byed //
NK009(ta)003:3945: seng lding phur pa zla gam gyis //
NK009(ta)003:3946: thams cad dbang du sdud par byed //
NK009(ta)003:3947: bswe shing phur pa rigs rgyas byed //
NK009(ta)003:3948: seng ldeng byang chub sems rgyas byed //
NK009(ta)003:3949: tsan+dana dmar po'i phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:3950: bu mo dbang du sdud par byed //
NK009(ta)003:3951: mdzo mos blon po dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)003:3952: bswe shing dmangs rigs dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)003:3953: zangs kyis rgyal po dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)003:3954: shing gis gdon rnams dbang du sdud //
NK009(ta)003:3957: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK009(ta)003:3960: ma rig mun pa'i d+r+wa ba sangs /
NK009(ta)003:3961: mkhyen pa'i ye shes pad+ma ltar rgyas pas rgyas /
NK009(ta)003:3962: kun ni 'das ma 'ongs da lta gsum /
NK009(ta)003:3963: sku ni ye shes kyi sku'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3965: sangs rgyas chos sku rten yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3969: kun ni 'das ma 'ongs da lta gsum /
NK009(ta)003:3970: sku ni ye shes kyi sku'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3972: sangs rgyas chos sku rten yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3980: sku yon tan gyi rten byed gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3981: ngang nyid rdo rje'i chos dbyings las /
NK009(ta)003:3983: chos sku'i ngo bo rdo rje stong nyid chos dbyings 'dus ma byas pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3986: de ka chos nyid yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:3987: ru bal po skye med kyi ngang nyid /
NK009(ta)003:3988: 'gag med rdo rje chos dbyings chos sku gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3989: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK009(ta)003:3991: ru pad+ma gdug pa 'dul bar 'bar ba de khro bo mi bzad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:3992: ru bi ma la gar gyi nyams dgu la zer /
NK009(ta)003:3993: ru bal po ma rig pa sel bas 'bar ba /
NK009(ta)003:3995: mi bzad pa 'khor yin gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:3996: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK009(ta)003:3998: ru pad+mas lha'i sku bskyed pa bstan /
NK009(ta)003:3999: ru bi ma las rim gyis bskyed pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4000: ru bal po rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4001: phur pa rdzas kyi dal tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4002: spyi don gsum pa khams gsum gis srog la dbang
NK009(ta)003:4003: bskur zhing srog gis ye shes sems dpa'i srog la
NK009(ta)003:4008: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK009(ta)003:4009: zhes pa sh+lo ka gcig go //
NK009(ta)003:4012: rigs lnga gdan tsho lnga spyi bo'i steng du spyan drangs ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4013: shar phyogs pa rnams kyis chu dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)003:4014: lho phyogs pas dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)003:4015: nub nas rdo rje'i dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)003:4016: byang nas dril bu'i dbang bskur /
NK009(ta)003:4017: dbus nas ming gi dbang bskur bar bsam pa ni bum pa'i dbang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4018: de nas rigs lnga yab yum rnams sbyor ba mdzad
NK009(ta)003:4019: pas sbyor mtshams nas byang sems byung bas bdag gi
NK009(ta)003:4020: spyi bo nas mar thim pas sdig sgrib dag pa
NK009(ta)003:4022: de nas rigs lnga de rnams rang gi spyi bo
NK009(ta)003:4023: nas mar thams cad 'dus te thim pa ni shes
NK009(ta)003:4024: rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4025: de'i dus su bde stong gi nyams rgyud la skyes pa ni dbang bzhi pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4026: de nas rigs lnga cha gcig yar log nas dbu rgyan du bsgom pa ni dbang rtags so //
NK009(ta)003:4027: de ni dus gsum bud+d+hasa bdag la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4028: dbang des s+pha ra na phata ces spros pas khams gsum sems can la phog go //
NK009(ta)003:4029: de rnams zhu ste lha rnams a /
NK009(ta)003:4035: de ram yam kham gis bsregs sbyangs pas dal gyi lhar gyur par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4036: de nas 'od zer de tshur 'dus te sam ha
NK009(ta)003:4037: ra na h'u zhes pas snying gi nang gi rta
NK009(ta)003:4038: mgrin la 'dus / dbang bskur bas bkrag dang ldan pa ni des srog la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4039: de nas rta mgrin yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pas byang sems de ye shes sems dpa' la thim /
NK009(ta)003:4041: bkrag dang ldan pas bkrag thams cad 'dus te rdo rje lte ba'i h'u la phog /
NK009(ta)003:4042: h'u de bkrag gzi mdangs dang ldan pa ni ye shes sems dpa'i srog la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4043: de las lcags kyi srog rtsa byug bar bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4044: de nas dal gsum gyi spyi bo dkar po re /
NK009(ta)003:4046: snying gar h'u sngon po re bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4047: de spros bsdus pas spyi bo rnam snang dkar po re /
NK009(ta)003:4048: mgrin par snang mtha' dmar po re /
NK009(ta)003:4049: snying gar mi bskyod ba sngon po re bsam pa ni dbang rtags so //
NK009(ta)003:4052: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK009(ta)003:4054: ru pad 'byung gis sems can gyi don du thabs bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4056: thabs mkhas pas 'gro don bya gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4058: thabs kyi spyod pas zin par gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4059: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK009(ta)003:4062: bsam pa byams pa lag len snying rje yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4064: theg chen la byams pa dang snying rje dgos gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4066: khyad par du gsang sngags la byams snying rje dgos gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4067: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad nas //
NK009(ta)003:4069: ru pad+ma sangs rgyas phrin las kyi ngo bo bskyed rdzogs /
NK009(ta)003:4070: nges tshig bud+d+ha'i phrin las gang zag gis las su byed pa /
NK009(ta)003:4071: dbye ba phrin las bzhi'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4074: ye shes rgyas na phrin las rdzogs zer /
NK009(ta)003:4076: zhi rgyas dbang drag gang 'dul gyis rdzogs par bya gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4077: dbang bskur thams cad 'dir stsol zhig /
NK009(ta)003:4079: ru pad+ma phyi dbang snang ba lhar shes na byin rlabs 'byung gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4080: ru bi ma la nang dbang snang srid sems su shes pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4081: ru bal po gsang dbang snang srid stong par rtogs na byin rlabs 'byung gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4083: spyi don bzhi pa ye shes kyi dal spyan drangs
NK009(ta)003:4084: shing mchod cing bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud blang
NK009(ta)003:4086: ye shes pa spyan drangs pa /
NK009(ta)003:4087: de la mchod pa brgyad 'bul ba /
NK009(ta)003:4089: mchod cing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4092: srid pa'i phur bu bsgrub pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4093: zhes pa sh+lo ka phyed dang gnyis so //
NK009(ta)003:4095: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od 'phros pas 'og min
NK009(ta)003:4096: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas rang dang 'dra
NK009(ta)003:4097: ba'i dal gsum mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK009(ta)003:4098: de la mchod pa 'bul ba la brgyad de /
NK009(ta)003:4099: dang po nam mkha' la phyag gis mchod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4100: bstim nas lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4101: ba lim ta gtor ma'i mchod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4102: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4103: rak+ta tshar gsum gyi mchod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4105: 'dod don gyi gsol ba gdab pa /
NK009(ta)003:4106: tshogs dang bstod pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4107: dang po nam mkha' la phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4108: nam mkha' na bzhugs pa la /
NK009(ta)003:4109: a ti p+au hoh zhes pas ye shes pa la phyag btsal /
NK009(ta)003:4110: ye shes pas pra t+aits+tsha hoh lan dngos grub byin par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4111: ye shes pa'i 'khor phur srung rnams kyis /
NK009(ta)003:4112: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ba ta nan gyis bdag
NK009(ta)003:4113: dam tshig pa la phyag lan btsal bar bsam mo
NK009(ta)003:4114: // gnyis pa bstims nas lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pa la /
NK009(ta)003:4118: hohs mi dgyes pa med par dgyes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4119: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas phyi yi lha mo bzhi spros la /
NK009(ta)003:4122: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he gan /
NK009(ta)003:4123: yang nang gyi lha mo spros la /
NK009(ta)003:4126: badz+ra g+airti h+r+aih badz+ra n+airti +aah yang 'dod yon gyi lha mo spros la /
NK009(ta)003:4131: zhes pas phyag rgya dang bcas pas mchod do //
NK009(ta)003:4133: srid pa'i phur bu bsgrub pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4135: ru pad 'byung ni srid pa sngar dang 'dra /
NK009(ta)003:4139: brag phug gnod sbyin gyi gnas /
NK009(ta)003:4141: dur khrod ma mo mkha' 'gro'i gnas so //
NK009(ta)003:4142: gnas der ye shes pa spyan drangs ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:4143: gang gis drangs na dam tshig pas drangs /
NK009(ta)003:4144: gang nas drangs na 'og min nas drangs /
NK009(ta)003:4145: gang du drangs na ting nge 'dzin gyi dal du drangs /
NK009(ta)003:4146: gang gi phyir drangs na phur bu sgrub pa'i phyir drangs so //
NK009(ta)003:4147: drangs nas sgrub pa la thun mong dang khyad par ro //
NK009(ta)003:4153: khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:4157: phyi ma ltar du sgrub pa d+ha ti /
NK009(ta)003:4158: nang sring mo ltar sgrub pa 'dus la /
NK009(ta)003:4159: gsang ba bran mo ltar sgrub pa bsdu yig go //
NK009(ta)003:4161: ging gnyis gcig gi sgrub pa /
NK009(ta)003:4163: ma ru rtse gcig gi sgrub pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4164: de'ang sngags re re la mgo gnon dang rang re'i sngags /
NK009(ta)003:4169: rang re'i ting nge 'dzin tshang dgos gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4171: srid pa gsum sku gsung thugs su sgrub gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4172: ru bal pos srid gsum chos skur sgrub gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4173: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:4176: dbang la rtogs pa chos nyid kyi dbang /
NK009(ta)003:4178: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4182: tha ma mig sman no gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4184: dngos grub sku gsung thugs kyi'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4185: ru bal po dngos grub 'das pa dang lo ka'i dngos grub gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4186: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK009(ta)003:4188: ru pad+ma ye shes ji lta ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4190: khro bo rngams shing brjod pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4191: ru bi ma la dbyings ye shes gdug pa 'dul du gshegs gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4193: ye shes yin la khro bo ma yin pa zhi ba'i rigs lnga lta bu dang /
NK009(ta)003:4194: ye shes ma yin la kho bo yin pa bdud dang srin po lta bu dang /
NK009(ta)003:4195: ye shes kyang ma yin la khro bo yang ma yin pa'i rigs drug sems can lta bu dang /
NK009(ta)003:4196: ye shes kyang yin la khro bo yang yin pa phur bu'i lha tshogs lta bu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4198: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK009(ta)003:4200: ru pad+ma ni thugs rje chen pos gshegs par zhu zer /
NK009(ta)003:4201: ru bi ma la gang gang gi don du gshegs gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4202: ru bal po byed pa'i tshig bzhi dang sbyar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4203: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang zhes pas /
NK009(ta)003:4206: tha ma rmi ltas ston pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4207: ru bi ma la rtags phyir /
NK009(ta)003:4209: ru bal po rtags lus yangs /
NK009(ta)003:4212: mtshan ma mi rtog pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4213: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK009(ta)003:4215: ru pad+ma bud+d+ha thob pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4216: ru bi ma la khams gsum sgrol ba'i phyir gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4217: ru bal po rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4218: ye shes pa spyan drangs pa tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4219: gsum pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4220: dam tshig chen pos gtso bo la dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4221: sprul pa chen pos phyogs bcu'i khro bo la dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4222: phyag brnyan chen pos mgo brnyan nyi shu la dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4223: shwa nas shwa na bzhi la dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4224: bdag nyid chen mos re ma t+ai la dbul sa bdag gis bswe mo bzhi la /
NK009(ta)003:4225: khyed kyi dam tshig dus ling+ga dbul lo //
NK009(ta)003:4226: lha rnams kyi ljags kyi sbu gus gsol bar bsam mo //
NK009(ta)003:4228: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4230: ru pad+ma sngon du ru tra sgrol tsa na /
NK009(ta)003:4231: bud+d+ha thams cad kyi sras kyi dam tshig ltar dus la bab par gyis gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4233: dus gsum gyi bud+d+ha'i thugs dam bskul ba'i dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4234: ru bal po sngon bi d+hi tsit+ta'i sems bskyed rtsa ba'i dus la bab zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:4235: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab /
NK009(ta)003:4237: ru pad+ma ru dra 'dul tsa na khro bo'i sprul
NK009(ta)003:4238: pa bye ba sa ya sprul pa'i dus la bab
NK009(ta)003:4239: gsungs / ru bi ma la lha yi dbang po brgya byin khro bcu sprul te bkye bas /
NK009(ta)003:4240: lha ma yin pham par bya'o zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:4241: ru bal po da lta'ang rnal 'byor pas bskul tsa na'ang de ltar sprul pa'o gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4242: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4244: ru pad+ma ru dra 'dul tsa na byi mo slas
NK009(ta)003:4245: mo rnams la phra men mgo lus mi mthun pa
NK009(ta)003:4246: mang po skyes pas btul ba'i dus la bab gsungs
NK009(ta)003:4248: sngon phyag rdor gyi gnod sbyin rgod ma kha btul bas /
NK009(ta)003:4249: kho ri ma la ya la bros pas /
NK009(ta)003:4250: phra men bkye ste bkug pa'i dus la bab gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4251: ru bal po nyi shu po las yang sprul sum sprul gyi dus la bab gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4252: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4254: ru pad+ma sngon dpal chen ye shes kyi ma mo
NK009(ta)003:4255: rnams 'phar spyang wa khyir sprul pa'i dus la bab
NK009(ta)003:4256: gsungs so // ru bi ma la /
NK009(ta)003:4257: g.ya' ri gangs kyi brag phug tu bse'i lha mo dam la btags pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4259: sngon gyi khas blangs kyi dus la bab gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4260: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4262: ru pad+ma 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma bud+d+ha'i
NK009(ta)003:4263: bstan pa'i bdag nyid yin pas dus la bab gsungs
NK009(ta)003:4265: skye ba lnga brgya la sprul pa lnga brgya 'byung bas /
NK009(ta)003:4266: de la sgrub thabs lnga brgya'i bdag nyid yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4267: ru bal po sems can gi srog dbugs kyi bdag mo yin pas bdag nyid zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:4268: sa bdag bse mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4270: ru pad+ma sngon du ru dra'i byi mo slas mo
NK009(ta)003:4271: yin pas dpal chen la bran du phul ba gsungs
NK009(ta)003:4273: chu mig byang chub ris su btul bas gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4274: ru bal po yul so so nas mthu che bas so gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4275: khyod kyi dam chig dus la bab /
NK009(ta)003:4277: ru pad+ma ging dang koo r+ai dbang phyug ma bdun sring bzhi la gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4278: ru bi ma la skyes bu ging 'bum phrag la gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4279: ru bal po rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang yan chad la gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4280: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4282: ru pad+ma sngon du ru dra btul tsa na mthu rtsal /
NK009(ta)003:4283: dbyung bar mdzad do zhes so //
NK009(ta)003:4285: sprul pa yang sprul gyis gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4286: ru bal po khams gsum dbang du bsdus la stong gsum zil gyis gnon gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4287: gtor ma dbul ba tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4288: bzhi pa sman mchod la lnga ste /
NK009(ta)003:4289: dang po sman gyi che ba brjod pa /
NK009(ta)003:4294: dang po che ba brjod pa'i /
NK009(ta)003:4295: dus su kha ram rnam gsum gyi dgongs pa la /
NK009(ta)003:4296: kha ram dang por snang srid mchod pa rdzas sngags bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4297: kha ram gnyis pas de yang bdud rtsi chen por bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4298: kha ram gsum pas dal gsum gyis gsol bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4299: sman mchod dngos kyi dus su sman phor du dpa' bo 'bru gsum bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4300: rnam dag zer tsa na h'u gi 'od kyis nyes skyon dag par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4301: bdud rtsi zer tsa na +aahzhu nas bdud rtsir song bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4302: dam rdzas zer tsa na zhu nas sha lnga bdud rtsi lngar song bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4303: mnyes mchod 'bul zer tsa na mnyes par 'bul /
NK009(ta)003:4304: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK009(ta)003:4305: zhes pas rnal 'byor pas de kha len 'dod pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4306: de nas bshags shing dngos grub blang ba'i skabs su /
NK009(ta)003:4307: sman gyi nang du bud+d+ha thams cad kyi sku'i ngo bo dkar po zhig bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4308: rang gi ya rkan la'ang dkar po zhig bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4310: mtheb srin gyis sman gyi de blang lce la bzhag pa /
NK009(ta)003:4311: ya rkan gyi dang 'grogs te song bas spyi bo
NK009(ta)003:4312: klad pa dung khang du rnam snang dkar po zhig
NK009(ta)003:4314: de ltar bud+d+ha'i gsung +aahdamara po sman phor dang ma rkan gnyis la bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4315: sngags tshig mtheb srin gyis blang ste mid pas /
NK009(ta)003:4316: mgrin par snang mtha' dmar po bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4317: de ltar bud+d+ha'i thugs h'u mi bskyod pa sngon po dang gong gi 'dra'o //
NK009(ta)003:4318: de nas smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4319: lnga pa rak+ta tshar gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4321: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK009(ta)003:4322: zhes pas dang po bka' nyan par byed pa'i ched du dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4323: gnyis pa bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs kyis dam can gnad la dbab pa'i phyir du dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4325: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:4327: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i ched du dbul /
NK009(ta)003:4328: dug lnga dug gsum gyi mchod pa'ang shugs la shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4330: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK009(ta)003:4332: ru pad+ma sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob tu ma ster bar gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4333: ru bi ma la chos nyid thob tu ma ster bar gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4334: ru bal po sems bkol du mi btub bar gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4335: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK009(ta)003:4346: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK009(ta)003:4355: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK009(ta)003:4357: ru pad+ma chos nyid rtogs nas nyon mongs pa bral bar gyis zer /
NK009(ta)003:4360: ru bal po lha'i grogs dang bral bar gyis zer /
NK009(ta)003:4361: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK009(ta)003:4363: ru pad+ma 'khor ba nas khug chos smrar chug zer /
NK009(ta)003:4365: bla khug smyo bas smrar chug zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:4366: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK009(ta)003:4368: ru pad+ma ye shes phob cig nyon mongs gzir zer /
NK009(ta)003:4372: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK009(ta)003:4374: ru pad+ma sems dbang du gyur nas zer /
NK009(ta)003:4377: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NK009(ta)003:4379: ru pad+ma rtogs pa'i bka' nyon zer /
NK009(ta)003:4382: sngags la bshad pa byas pas byin rlabs tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4384: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK009(ta)003:4386: ru pad+ma sngon ru dra'i bran dang bka' nyan dpal chen la phul bas gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4388: bar du pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis dam la btags pas zer /
NK009(ta)003:4389: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4391: ru pad+ma sngon dpal chen gyi spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa bzhin zer /
NK009(ta)003:4393: pad 'byung spyan sngar dam bcas pa bzhin zer ro //
NK009(ta)003:4394: mngon spyod phrin las rdzogs par mdzod //
NK009(ta)003:4396: ru pad+ma mngon du thob par mdzod zer /
NK009(ta)003:4400: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK009(ta)003:4402: ru pad 'byung gdug pa nyon mongs /
NK009(ta)003:4407: lha'am gnod sbyin bdud kyang rung //
NK009(ta)003:4409: ru pad+ma lha dam la 'da' ba bdud yin zer /
NK009(ta)003:4411: lha klu bdud dang dri za'ang rung zer /
NK009(ta)003:4412: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK009(ta)003:4413: nga la sngags kyi bka' bden pas //
NK009(ta)003:4414: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK009(ta)003:4416: ru pad+mas mthu sems bsgyur ba rdzu 'phrul ya ma
NK009(ta)003:4417: zung ston pa'i nus pa med par gyis shig pa'o
NK009(ta)003:4419: drug pa sbyor sgrol gyi p+au dza ni /
NK009(ta)003:4420: sbyor ba ni khro bo yab yum sbyor /
NK009(ta)003:4421: sgrol ba ni dgra dang bgegs sgrol ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4422: de yang lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la yab lnga /
NK009(ta)003:4423: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga yum lngar bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4424: yab kyi mkha' mi dmigs pa las h'u las rdo rje dbal dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4425: yum gyi mkha' mi dmigs pa las /
NK009(ta)003:4426: e las lcags kyi gtun khung gru gsum par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4427: dgra bgegs bkugs la nang du bcug /
NK009(ta)003:4428: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i dbyings //
NK009(ta)003:4430: lag pa rdo rje bsdams pas kha tham brjod cing dgra bgegs phye mar brdungs pas /
NK009(ta)003:4431: rgyu gti mug las 'bras bu shar smin pa ka p+aa la khengs pa lnga byung /
NK009(ta)003:4432: gtso bo bdag rtsa ba'i dal la phul /
NK009(ta)003:4433: lhag ma dal gnyis kyis gsol bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4434: yang kha tham bdun gyis brdungs pas /
NK009(ta)003:4435: rgyu 'dod chags las 'bras bu khrag tu smin pa ka p+aa la lnga byung /
NK009(ta)003:4436: gtso bor khro bo la phul /
NK009(ta)003:4437: lhag ma dkyil 'khor gnyis kyis lhag med kyis zos par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4438: yang kha tham bdun gyis brdungs pas /
NK009(ta)003:4439: rgyu zhe sdang las 'bras bu rus par smin pa ka p+aa la lnga byung /
NK009(ta)003:4440: gtso bo phur pa rdzas la phul /
NK009(ta)003:4441: lhag ma dal thams cad kyis gsol bar bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4442: de nas lha thams cad dgyes pas ha ha zhes gsungs so //
NK009(ta)003:4443: de ni dug gsum gyi mchod pa dngos yin no //
NK009(ta)003:4445: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK009(ta)003:4447: ru pad 'byung gis mtshan ma'i tho gtun gyis 'brub khung du brdung /
NK009(ta)003:4448: dbyings kyi tho gtun gyis dngos po brdung /
NK009(ta)003:4449: thabs shes kyi tho gtun gyis yum gyi mkhar brdung /
NK009(ta)003:4451: phyi'i dus na rdo rje tho ba /
NK009(ta)003:4452: nang gi dus na thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes /
NK009(ta)003:4453: gsang ba'i dus na yab kyi rdo rje'o //
NK009(ta)003:4454: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK009(ta)003:4456: ru pad+ma bstan pa la gnod pa zer /
NK009(ta)003:4458: ru'i sku la gnod pa zer /
NK009(ta)003:4460: sngags 'chang gi sku la gnod pa zer /
NK009(ta)003:4461: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK009(ta)003:4463: ru pad+ma gsang ba'i rdo rje la byang sems kyi me dbal can nam /
NK009(ta)003:4464: phyag mtshan gyi rdo rje la ye shes kyi me dbal can gyis gnod byed kyi snying bsregs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4465: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK009(ta)003:4469: 'dod chags kyi ngag ye shes kyi mes rdul du rlog zer /
NK009(ta)003:4470: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK009(ta)003:4473: khro mo kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai'i mkha' dbyings la bya /
NK009(ta)003:4474: rdo rje tho bas brdung bar bya //
NK009(ta)003:4475: zhes pa gsang ba'i rdo rje ste /
NK009(ta)003:4477: lha yang rung ste brlag par bya //
NK009(ta)003:4479: lha'i bu'i bdud dam tshangs pa'am bish+nu'ang gnod na brlag par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4481: bdun pa 'dod don gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4482: rak+ta dang phud bsres pa dbul zhing /
NK009(ta)003:4483: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4485: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
NK009(ta)003:4487: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK009(ta)003:4488: zhes pas bsdus pa gang rung bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4489: dam tshig chen po drug ni bshad zin /
NK009(ta)003:4490: 'bru la bshad na bar pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4491: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK009(ta)003:4493: phyi rabs rten gyi gang zag go //
NK009(ta)003:4494: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK009(ta)003:4496: ru pad+ma kun rdzob byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4497: don dam byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'o gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4500: chub pa po der gnyis med du sems bskyed gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4501: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa //
NK009(ta)003:4504: dus gsum mnyam nyid du rtogs na rgyal ba de'i gdung lta ba rtogs pas zin pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4506: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung rdo rje gzhon nus /
NK009(ta)003:4508: de'i gdung phur srung yan chad kyis gsungs so /
NK009(ta)003:4509: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK009(ta)003:4511: ru pad 'byung rig 'dzin bzhi'i rigs 'og ma rnams kyis bzung /
NK009(ta)003:4512: ru bi ma la rig pa rnal 'byor pas bzung ngo gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4513: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK009(ta)003:4515: ru pad 'byung bstan pa la gnod pa sngags 'chang
NK009(ta)003:4516: la gdug pa de dgra dang bgegs yin pas gsungs
NK009(ta)003:4517: / bdud dang bar du gcod pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4519: ru pad 'byung m+aa ra zhes pas bdud des dge ba'i bar du gcod pa yin gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4521: des mtho ris thar pa la bar du gcod zer /
NK009(ta)003:4524: ru pad+ma dngos grub sku gsung thugs kyi 'phrog pa de 'tshe ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4525: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK009(ta)003:4528: chen po ye shes dang ldan pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4530: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK009(ta)003:4532: skad cig thang cig yud tsam la /
NK009(ta)003:4533: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4534: zhes pas che mthong chung mthong sgrol ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4536: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK009(ta)003:4538: nyon mongs ye shes lngar bsgral lo //
NK009(ta)003:4539: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)003:4541: bud+d+ha dang sngags 'chang gi bka' las 'das pa'i chad pas khong nas me 'bar ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4542: kha nas khrag skyug pa 'ong ba chos nyid yin no //
NK009(ta)003:4544: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK009(ta)003:4546: ru pad+ma rdo rje thugs skye shi med pa /
NK009(ta)003:4547: de snod min la gsang ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4548: sdig can gang gi 'da' byed pa //
NK009(ta)003:4550: ru pad+ma rdo rje 'chang gi bka' las 'da' ba'i dam nyams pa de'o //
NK009(ta)003:4551: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK009(ta)003:4553: ru pad+ma ye shes kyi stobs kyis bdud 'joms pa zer /
NK009(ta)003:4554: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK009(ta)003:4556: klad pa byang sems kyi mtsho yin pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4557: yan lag gi dang po mgo bo yin pa khos zhes pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4558: ru pad 'byung dngos 'dzin gyi mgo khos gsungs /
NK009(ta)003:4559: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK009(ta)003:4561: ru pad+ma chos nyid bden pa'i bka' la nyon /
NK009(ta)003:4565: de nas bstod pa gnyis gnyis bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4566: bsnyen pas dngos grub kyi bcud blang ba ni /
NK009(ta)003:4572: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)003:4573: zhes pas tshig bzhis dbye ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4574: bar du 'dzab bzlas pa la gsum /
NK009(ta)003:4576: nang ltar gsang ba ltar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4577: de re re la sku'i bzlas pa /
NK009(ta)003:4583: drag po nyi zer gyi char dbab pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:4584: bdag gi spyi bo nas bud+d+ha k+ai la ya'i thugs ka nas /
NK009(ta)003:4585: 'od smug nag dbyibs phur pa 'dra ba /
NK009(ta)003:4587: chung ba yungs 'bru tsam 'phros pas gang la phog pas nyal nyal 'gro bar bsam zhing /
NK009(ta)003:4588: bud+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya bzla /
NK009(ta)003:4589: 'od zer phyir 'phros phyi ltar bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4590: spyi bo nas bzlas pas nang sku ltar bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4592: de ltar lkog ma'i pad+ma k+ai la yas +aahpad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya bzla /
NK009(ta)003:4593: 'od zer dmar nag dbyibs phur ba 'dra ba che chung gong gi 'gres /
NK009(ta)003:4595: yang thugs kyi badz+ra k+ai la yas h'u badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bzla /
NK009(ta)003:4596: 'od zer mthing nag phur pa 'dra ba spros /
NK009(ta)003:4598: yang lte ba nas rat+na k+ai la yas s+w+aa rat+na k+ai li k+ai la ya bzla /
NK009(ta)003:4601: gsang gnas nas karma k+ai la yas h+aa kar+m+aa k+ai li k+ai la ya bzla /
NK009(ta)003:4602: 'od zer ljang nag phrin las kyi bzlas pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4603: de nas nang gi bzlas pa 'od zer nang du 'phros pas nad gdon bsregs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4605: 'od rtsa sbubs dang snying dkar nag tu 'phros pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4610: dang po ga na tshogs la brgyad de /
NK009(ta)003:4618: de nas dam tshig gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:4619: dang po tshogs pa gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4622: 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs so //
NK009(ta)003:4623: de yang dang po lha rang yang phyi nang bsrer mi btub ste /
NK009(ta)003:4624: lha mthun pa zhig bsgom dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:4625: gnyis pa mi rang yang mi mthun pa mi rung ste dam tshig gtsang ba zhig dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:4626: gsum pa longs spyod kyang ngan chung bas mi thub ste /
NK009(ta)003:4627: bzang po gya nom pa rmad du byung ba dgos so //
NK009(ta)003:4628: gnyis pa gsog pa la gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4629: gnas dur khrod lta bur grub pa thob pa'i bla ma gsog /
NK009(ta)003:4630: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo gsog /
NK009(ta)003:4631: 'dod yon lnga'i longs spyod gsog pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4632: gsum pa bsang ba gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4637: rang la'ang ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4638: cho ga las ma tshang ba yod pas /
NK009(ta)003:4639: a mri ta rang la gtor bas dag pas bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4640: gnyis pa mched lcam la nyams grib yod pas a mri ta gtor bas dag par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4641: gsum pa tshogs la'ang ma dag pa nyams pa yod
NK009(ta)003:4642: pas a mri ta gtor bas dag par bsam mo
NK009(ta)003:4643: // bzhi pa sbyang ba gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4644: snod thod pa stong gsum tsam du bsam la /
NK009(ta)003:4645: nang gi tshogs kyi dngos po'i steng du /
NK009(ta)003:4648: kham las chu byung bkrus par bsam mo //
NK009(ta)003:4649: lnga pa brlab pa la gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4650: tshogs kyi steng du h'u byung bas sngo ding song /
NK009(ta)003:4652: byung bas dkar po shel ltar dwangs par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4653: drug pa bskyed pa gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4654: dang po mchod pa'i dus su 'dod yon lngar bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4655: bshags pa'i dus su ye shes lngar bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4656: bstab pa'i dus su dgra bgegs kyi don snying lngar bskyed pa'o /
NK009(ta)003:4657: 'dod lha ni bdud rtsi 'khyil bas bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4658: de yang tshogs kyi steng du a las zla ba bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4659: de'i steng du yab lnga'i sa bon +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4660: nyi ma'i steng du yum lnga'i m+aum m+aum m+aam p+y+aam t+aam bskyed /
NK009(ta)003:4661: de las yab yum bskyed la /
NK009(ta)003:4662: +aahmh'u ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aih
NK009(ta)003:4663: zhes brjod pas yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pas thig
NK009(ta)003:4664: le byang sems su zhu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4665: spris ma du chags pa la 'dod yon lnga'i lha mo 'phro bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4667: bla ma rdo rje 'chang rnams dang /
NK009(ta)003:4668: yi dam dal lha rnams dang /
NK009(ta)003:4669: ma mo mkha' 'gro dpa' bo dpa' mo rnams la 'bul lo //
NK009(ta)003:4670: brgyad pa dam tshig la bzhi /
NK009(ta)003:4676: sems 'khrugs pa'i rtsod pa mi bya /
NK009(ta)003:4677: gzung 'dzin skye ba'i 'khrul gtam mi bya /
NK009(ta)003:4678: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bags btsog mi bsrung ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4679: gnyis pa tshogs la gzhan gyi che ste bdag gi chung mi bya /
NK009(ta)003:4680: na ning bzang ste da lo ngan pa mi bya /
NK009(ta)003:4681: kha sang mang ste de ri nyung bar mi bya /
NK009(ta)003:4683: tshogs mthong ba'i tshe bza' yi snyam du mi bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4684: btung gi snyam du mi bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4685: zhim gyi snyam du mi bsam pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4686: bzhi pa mi 'bral ba gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:4689: sems rdzogs rim dang mi 'bral ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4690: de nas lag len la rtsa rgyud las /
NK009(ta)003:4691: bgegs bskrad byin rlabs spyan drangs dang //
NK009(ta)003:4692: mchod dang skong ba zlog pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:4693: stod kyi las su shes par bya //
NK009(ta)003:4694: bstod dang 'bul dang bshags pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4695: smon lam rgya chen btab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:4696: smad kyi las su shes par bya //
NK009(ta)003:4698: lag len las byang ltar du shes par bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4699: ga na tshogs mchod tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4700: de yan chad stod las bla na med pa'i byang chub sgrub pa rdzogs so //
NK009(ta)003:4702: // 'di man chad smad las dgra bgegs tshar gcod pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:4703: rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:4704: spyi don lnga pa gab pa'i sngags drug /
NK009(ta)003:4705: tshe lung khrus lung gis kha bskangs te gdab pa'i las bya /
NK009(ta)003:4707: dang po gab pa'i sngags drug bstan pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4708: tshe lung khrus lung bstan pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4710: dang po smad las 'di rnams dgra bgegs rtsad nas
NK009(ta)003:4711: bcad pa'i phyir rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa ni
NK009(ta)003:4712: / dgra bgegs thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing bcu la 'dus te /
NK009(ta)003:4714: sngags 'chang gi sku la bsdo ba /
NK009(ta)003:4715: dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang smad pa sogs zhing bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4716: phur pa khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK009(ta)003:4717: dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4718: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4720: theg chen chos la dmod pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4721: bla ma'i sku la bsdo ba dang //
NK009(ta)003:4722: rdo rje'i nang du dbyen spyod dang //
NK009(ta)003:4723: sgrub la bar chad byed pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4724: gang zhig dam las log pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4725: snying rje med pa'i srin po dang //
NK009(ta)003:4726: mu stegs log ltar gtong ba dang //
NK009(ta)003:4727: sgrub pa po la do bsdo ba /
NK009(ta)003:4729: zhes pas dgra bgegs de rnams kyi rgyas bshad phur pa gsang rgyud nas bshad pas der ltos shig /
NK009(ta)003:4730: de yang rgyud kyi dgongs pa gab pa'i sngags drug 'di la bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:4731: mngon spyod thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba yin pas kun gyi sna 'dren du btang ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4732: sgrub pa thams cad kyi ngo bo yin pas dkyus kyi khong khrar btang ba dang /
NK009(ta)003:4733: las thams cad kyi mjug sdud yin pas smon lam gyi tshul du gdab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:4734: drag sngags yin pas ngan sngags su byas te srog la 'khor lo bskor ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4736: lha dpral gnas nas dgug pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4737: rnam shes gzugs bstim byad du gzhug /
NK009(ta)003:4738: smyor gzhug rdul du rlag pa dang //
NK009(ta)003:4739: sha khrag zhal du bstab na dgyes //
NK009(ta)003:4742: 'di la rgyud sde ma mthong ba kha cig lnga lnga bdun bdun byed pa 'dug kyang /
NK009(ta)003:4743: rtsa rgyud kyi dgongs pa bcu bcu ste drug cu tham par bshad do //
NK009(ta)003:4745: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha drug /
NK009(ta)003:4746: gdab pa gnad kyi phur pa drug /
NK009(ta)003:4748: bskul bar bya ba'i pho nya drug /
NK009(ta)003:4750: bsag par bya ba'i rdzas drug /
NK009(ta)003:4751: bzla bar bya ba'i sngags drug /
NK009(ta)003:4752: bca' bar bya ba'i phyag rgya drug /
NK009(ta)003:4754: gdab pa'i smon lam drug ste bcu'o //
NK009(ta)003:4755: de las dang po lha dang phral ba la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4756: gnyen po stobs kyi lha ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ste /
NK009(ta)003:4759: 'jig rten las kyi lha ni rdo rje legs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4760: gnyis pa gdab pa gnad kyi phur pa /
NK009(ta)003:4762: gsum pa gdab pa'i gnas ni spyi gtsug tu gdab ste /
NK009(ta)003:4763: gnam gyi 'ju thag bcad pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)003:4764: bzhi pa bskul ba'i pho nya ni /
NK009(ta)003:4765: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4768: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK009(ta)003:4770: drug la bsags pa'i rdzas ni /
NK009(ta)003:4777: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hohche ge
NK009(ta)003:4778: mo m+aa ra ya ha sa ya ra h+r+ai da
NK009(ta)003:4779: ya na sarba big+h+n+aana ban+d+ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:4781: brgyad pa bca' ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK009(ta)003:4782: dud pas bdug pa'i tshul te /
NK009(ta)003:4785: bdag gi thugs ka nas sprul pa yang sprul mang
NK009(ta)003:4786: po gu gul gyi dud pa thogs pa mang po
NK009(ta)003:4787: byung ste bdug pas dgra bo lha dang phral te
NK009(ta)003:4788: mi med pa'i grong stong pa'am /
NK009(ta)003:4789: byi khyur rdo 'phangs pas gzhan 'phur te phog pa
NK009(ta)003:4790: de kho na gcig pur lus pa ltar bsam mo
NK009(ta)003:4792: gtso bo rdo rje gzhon nu nas phur srung yul
NK009(ta)003:4793: phyogs lha klu rnams brjod la dgra bo dam nyams
NK009(ta)003:4794: che ge mo 'di pho lha dang phrol zhig /
NK009(ta)003:4800: gnyis pa gzugs la dbab pa la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4801: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha mi g.yo mgon po ste /
NK009(ta)003:4804: 'jig rten las kyi lha ni yam shud dmar po'o //
NK009(ta)003:4807: gsum pa gdab gnas ni rkang pa'i mthil du gdab ste sa'i rten phur phyung ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4809: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4812: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK009(ta)003:4815: mtshe nag yungs nag yungs kar rgyal po yug sa mo'i zhabs ma'o //
NK009(ta)003:4817: a we sha ya a we sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:4821: thugs ka'i 'od kyis gzas po bkug la ling+ga la bstim /
NK009(ta)003:4823: lha rnams brjod la dgra bo che ge mo khug cig phob cig bstim zhig ces pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4824: gsum pa byad du gzhugs pa la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4825: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha khams gsum rnam rgyal te /
NK009(ta)003:4828: 'jig rten las kyi lha ni klu'i rgyal po'o //
NK009(ta)003:4829: gnyis pa ni mchog phur ro //
NK009(ta)003:4830: gsum pa ni gsang gnas su gdab ste skye ba dgu brgyud bcad pa'i phyir ro //
NK009(ta)003:4831: bzhi pa bskul ba'i pho nya ni /
NK009(ta)003:4832: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4835: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK009(ta)003:4838: bal tshon sna lnga skud pa dkar nag gsum rnams so //
NK009(ta)003:4844: rang gi thugs ka nas zhags pa thogs pa mang
NK009(ta)003:4845: po byung ste gru gu thul du bcings par bsam
NK009(ta)003:4847: lha tshogs kyi rjes la lha'i byad du chug cig klu'i byad du chug gcig /
NK009(ta)003:4848: gnod sbyin gyi byad du chug cig /
NK009(ta)003:4849: ma mo'i byad du chug cig /
NK009(ta)003:4851: bzhi pa smyor gzhug pa la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4852: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha rta mgrin te /
NK009(ta)003:4855: 'jig rten las kyi lha ni rgyal po be dkar ro //
NK009(ta)003:4856: gnyis pa ni phur pa tsan+dana no //
NK009(ta)003:4857: gsum pa gnas ni lce'i dkyil du gdab ste ngag 'joms pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4858: bzhi pa bskul ba'i pho nya ni /
NK009(ta)003:4859: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4861: rings par khug la smyor chug cig /
NK009(ta)003:4867: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4871: snying gnas 'od tsh+wa tsh+wa lta bu 'phros /
NK009(ta)003:4875: bu ga dgu nas khrag 'dzag par bsgom /
NK009(ta)003:4877: dgra bo che ge mo smyor chug /
NK009(ta)003:4881: lnga pa rdul du brlag pa la bcu ste /
NK009(ta)003:4882: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha dbyug sngon can te /
NK009(ta)003:4883: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:4885: las kyi lha bdud kyis gdung ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4887: gsum pa snying dkar nag mtshams su gdab ste sems kyi dbyings phyung ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:4889: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:4891: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK009(ta)003:4895: rdo rje'i tho ba sogs so //
NK009(ta)003:4897: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4901: snying ga nas tho ba thogs pa mang pos brdung bar bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4903: dgra bo che ge mo rdul du rlog /
NK009(ta)003:4907: drug pa zhal du bstab pa la bcu /
NK009(ta)003:4908: dang po gnyen po stobs kyi lha stobs po che ste /
NK009(ta)003:4911: las kyi lha btsan gyis btab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4913: gsum pa gnas ni lte ba ste bskyed pa'i sa bon gzhom pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4915: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab /
NK009(ta)003:4917: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis /
NK009(ta)003:4919: drug pa rdzas e gru gsum du ling+ga bskyur ba'am /
NK009(ta)003:4920: yang na zhal du bstab bam thod ngan du gzhug go //
NK009(ta)003:4922: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:4927: h'u gsum gyis gtso bo zhal du gsol /
NK009(ta)003:4928: phata gsum gyis khro bo'i zhal du gsol /
NK009(ta)003:4929: ha ha has dal gsum dgyes par bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4930: bcu pa dgra bo che ge mo khro bo khro
NK009(ta)003:4931: mo'i zhal du stob ces lha thams cad la sbyar
NK009(ta)003:4932: ro // de nas ling+ga de'i mgo bo la mnan pa bya /
NK009(ta)003:4933: ro stod la sbyin sreg bya /
NK009(ta)003:4935: nang khrol lha'i zhal du stob bo //
NK009(ta)003:4941: gnyis pa tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pas mthar dbyung ba la bzhi ste /
NK009(ta)003:4942: gzas pa po'i khrus lung dang rnal 'byor pa bdag gi tshe lung ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4943: dang po kho'i khrus lung la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:4946: dgongs pa rnam pa gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:4947: dang po gsal ba gsum ni /
NK009(ta)003:4948: dang po badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la yas bdag rdo rje gzhon nur gsal /
NK009(ta)003:4949: sarba big+h+n+aana ban+d+ha h'u phata kyis phur pa sras mchog tu gsal /
NK009(ta)003:4950: yang badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya tshar gcig gis gzas pa po dngos su gsal bar byas te /
NK009(ta)003:4951: k+ai la yar dzahmh'u bam hohbatagasa pa brjod pas /
NK009(ta)003:4952: sras mchog gi phyag tha ma na las thams cad
NK009(ta)003:4953: pa'i sras mchog sku stod sol dum bcag pa 'dra
NK009(ta)003:4954: ba / sku smad phur pa dmar lhang nge ba g.yas lcags kyu /
NK009(ta)003:4955: g.yon phur pa bsnams pa sde /
NK009(ta)003:4956: dpag chen gyis mda' bzhin song ste /
NK009(ta)003:4957: gzas pa po'i gnas su skar mda' ltung ba ltar bab ste /
NK009(ta)003:4958: de'i snying ga nas lcags kyus bzung /
NK009(ta)003:4959: g.yon gyi phur bus mi zhan mi drag par phur bus 'debs kyin /
NK009(ta)003:4960: sdong gog drud pa bzhin du du ru ru yong ba ling+ga la bstim mo //
NK009(ta)003:4961: nya bo la bstim pa gal che'o //
NK009(ta)003:4962: de ltar gsum bo mi gsal na ci nyes she na /
NK009(ta)003:4964: bdag rdo rje gzhon nur mi gsal na ldog /
NK009(ta)003:4965: phur pa sras mchog tu mi gsal na rdugs gzas
NK009(ta)003:4966: pa po dngos su mi gsal na 'byam 'gro ba'o
NK009(ta)003:4967: // de nas dgongs pa gsum la /
NK009(ta)003:4968: a dkar bya dkar gyi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)003:4969: thugs rje 'brel thag gi dgongs pa /
NK009(ta)003:4970: gdung ba lu gu rgyud kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4972: lam h'u lam gi sngags lan gcig brjod pas dal
NK009(ta)003:4973: gsum po'i spyi bor h'u ka ra dkar po re
NK009(ta)003:4974: bsam / de'i spyi bor a dkar po re bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4975: phur bu'i rtse mor yang a dkar po re bsam /
NK009(ta)003:4976: gzas pa po'i snying gar yang a dkar po re bsam pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4977: a dkar bya dkar gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:4978: de nas lam gyi sngags lan gcig brjod pas h'u ka ra yab yum dang /
NK009(ta)003:4979: a zhu bas dal gsum bdag gi lus rkyal grod
NK009(ta)003:4980: zhos bkang ba ltar song bas sdig sgrib dag par
NK009(ta)003:4981: bsam / de nas phur pa nas gang gis ma reg pa tsam du bsgril la /
NK009(ta)003:4982: snying gar bsgril bas phur rtse'i a las 'od 'phros /
NK009(ta)003:4983: a phra mo yungs kar tsam 'phros /
NK009(ta)003:4984: kho'i snying ga'i a las kyang 'od 'phros te /
NK009(ta)003:4986: gzas pa po'i sdig pa thams cad dag par bsgom pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:4988: sngags bzlas shing yun bsring ngo //
NK009(ta)003:4989: de bdag dang gzas pa po phur pa gsum dgongs pa gcig gis 'brel /
NK009(ta)003:4991: chos nyid gcig gis 'brel bas na thugs rje'i 'brel thag gi dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4992: de yang snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)003:4994: spyir sems can thams cad snying rjes mi gtong /
NK009(ta)003:4995: bye brag tu gzas pa po snying rjes mi gtong /
NK009(ta)003:4996: kho 'khor bar mi gtong bas na gdung ba lu gu rgyud kyi 'brel ba'i dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK009(ta)003:4999: dang po byung tshor gyi sgo bkag pa /
NK009(ta)003:5000: gnyis pa sems kyi dbyings phyung ba /
NK009(ta)003:5001: gsum pa kun gzhi rtsad nas bcad pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:5003: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya che ge mo sarba big+h+n+aana ban+d+ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5004: ces brjod cing phur pa nas gang ma reg tsam
NK009(ta)003:5005: du mig la bsgril bas mig gzugs kyi byung tshor
NK009(ta)003:5006: bkag rna ba la bsgril bas rna ba sgra yi
NK009(ta)003:5007: byug tshor bkag / de bzhin du /
NK009(ta)003:5010: lus reg byung tshor bkag nas sgo lnga'i rnam shes
NK009(ta)003:5011: de sbra dkar chon thag gtub pa bzhin du kun
NK009(ta)003:5012: gzhi la 'ub 'dus pa bzhin bsam pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:5013: gnyis pa sems kyi dbyings phyung ba la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5018: sngags bzlas shing phur pa ri rab kyis basngigasa pas
NK009(ta)003:5019: kho'i sha khrag dang snying dkar nag 'bral ba ni
NK009(ta)003:5021: de nas phur bu'i 'od kyis snying dkar nag gi
NK009(ta)003:5022: mtshams na khrag gi sbal pa mthe bong tsam zhig
NK009(ta)003:5023: yod pa bsreg / de'i nang na dwangs ma rnam pa gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)003:5024: khrag gi dwangs ma mtshal lcog la dang 'dra ba /
NK009(ta)003:5025: rtsa'i dwangs ma rgyus pa klad pa 'dra ba /
NK009(ta)003:5026: dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og tu sbas pa'i rlangs pa tsam gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)003:5027: de gsum gyi dbus na kun gzhi'i shes pa yi
NK009(ta)003:5028: ge a thung gi tshul du sems can thams cad
NK009(ta)003:5029: la yod pas / yang sngags bzlas shing phur pa bcings pas /
NK009(ta)003:5030: sems de rnams kyi dbus su phur pa sleb pa ni gnad sleb pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:5031: de nas sngags brjod cing phur pa bcings pas kho'i rnam shes a thung du yod pa de /
NK009(ta)003:5032: rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'am /
NK009(ta)003:5033: bye tshan la mar 'du ba lta bu phur pa'i
NK009(ta)003:5034: rtse mo la 'dus pa ni gsum pa tog blangs
NK009(ta)003:5035: ba zhes bya'o // de nas de'i shul du phur pa gzhan zhig yod na btab la bzhag ste /
NK009(ta)003:5036: kho'i rnam shes la ldog pa med par byas pa
NK009(ta)003:5037: ni gsum pa kun gzhi rtsad nas bcad pa zhes
NK009(ta)003:5038: bya'o // de nas phur pa'i rtse mo la kho'i
NK009(ta)003:5039: rnam shes a bkrag dang ldan pa rig pa tshe
NK009(ta)003:5040: dang bsod nams dang bcas te tshur bdag la bstim
NK009(ta)003:5041: bya'o // ste / lam h'u lam lan gsum brjod
NK009(ta)003:5042: de bdag gi gnas gsum du reg pa kho'i tshe
NK009(ta)003:5043: dang bsod nams thams cad bdag la thim pas /
NK009(ta)003:5044: bdag bkrag dang gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsam pa ni bdag gi tshe lung ngo //
NK009(ta)003:5045: dper na me 'bar ba la shing bsnan pa dang 'dra'o //
NK009(ta)003:5046: bdag nyid tshe dang bsod nams dang ldan par 'gyur ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:5047: des ni kho'i tshe dang bsod nams thob pas bdag kyang mi pham la /
NK009(ta)003:5048: kho'ang sgrib pa dag pas mi pham ste gnyis ka 'tshengs nus pa'i mu yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5049: de nas phur pa'i rtse mo gyen la bstan la gnas spar ba'i cho ga bya sde /
NK009(ta)003:5050: lag mthil ya gcig gis phur pa'i mgo nas gyen la gdab pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:5051: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi rlung har te byung bas btegs /
NK009(ta)003:5052: a a zhes sngags bzlas pa gsum gyis kho'i rnam
NK009(ta)003:5053: shes a thung de me stag yar ba ltar song
NK009(ta)003:5054: ste / rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i sbyor mtshams su song ste /
NK009(ta)003:5055: rigs lnga'i sras su skye bar yang bsam /
NK009(ta)003:5056: skye'ang skye bas na rten 'brel gyi shugs yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5057: chos nyid kyi bden pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5058: de ni gnas spar ba'i cho ga bya ba gsang sngags kyi khyad chos yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5059: phur pa de btab nas gzhan 'debs pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:5060: g.yag ro la mda' tshab byed pa 'dra'o //
NK009(ta)003:5061: des na tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pa ma shes na ngan sngags dang khyad med /
NK009(ta)003:5062: gnas spar ba'i cho ga ma shes na bshan pa
NK009(ta)003:5063: dag khyad med ces slob dpon pad+mas gsungs pa'i don
NK009(ta)003:5064: no // tshe lung khrus lung tshar ro //
NK009(ta)003:5065: gsum pa gdab pa'i las bstan pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:5067: gtso bo phur pa blangs nas ni //
NK009(ta)003:5068: yi ge gsum gyis byin brlabs nas //
NK009(ta)003:5069: bdag nyid bsrung ba'i tshe phur bya //
NK009(ta)003:5071: gtso bo'i phur pa bdag nyid kyi srog lta bu yin pas byin brlabs byas /
NK009(ta)003:5072: mchod bstod byas kyin bzhugs su gsol /
NK009(ta)003:5074: de ltar bdag lus tshags tshud nas //
NK009(ta)003:5075: gzhan gyi lus sems dbral ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:5076: khro bo bcu yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:5077: lus kyi gnas bcu dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)003:5078: sgo ma bzhi yi phur pa yis //
NK009(ta)003:5079: lus kyi mtsho bzhi dag tu gdab //
NK009(ta)003:5080: mi bzad phur pa drug po yis //
NK009(ta)003:5081: gnas drug po la gdab par bya //
NK009(ta)003:5083: spyir sgrub phur brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK009(ta)003:5084: lha phur lnga bcu rtsa gcig /
NK009(ta)003:5085: gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK009(ta)003:5086: mgyogs phur brgyad cu tham pa /
NK009(ta)003:5087: phur pa sil bu la grangs med /
NK009(ta)003:5089: de rnams bsag par bya ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5090: 'dir gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig la /
NK009(ta)003:5091: khro bo bcu'i phur pa bcu /
NK009(ta)003:5092: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa bzhi ste bcu bzhi /
NK009(ta)003:5093: mi bzad pa'i drug ste nyi shu tham pa /
NK009(ta)003:5094: sras mchog badz+ra 'dus pa'i phur pa dang nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK009(ta)003:5095: dang po bskul ba'i pho nya ni /
NK009(ta)003:5096: dam tshig cen po'i dus la bab //
NK009(ta)003:5098: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK009(ta)003:5099: ces pa'i bar du bskul la /
NK009(ta)003:5100: gsal ba gsum dang ldan pas /
NK009(ta)003:5101: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya na m+aahs man+ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nan /
NK009(ta)003:5102: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5103: ch+gee mo m+aa ra ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5105: rnam par rgyal ba'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5106: ma byin par len pa'i gnas yin pas mig gnyis la gdab bo //
NK009(ta)003:5107: spyir rdo rje phur pa la dbu gnon gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5108: de bzhin nyid don gyi dbu gnon /
NK009(ta)003:5109: k+ai la ya sngags kyi dbu gnon /
NK009(ta)003:5110: dus la bab pa tshig gi dbu gnon yin pas k+ai la ya kun la 'agre'o //
NK009(ta)003:5111: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5112: dbyug sngon can gyi phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5113: log par lta ba'i gnas yin pas sna gnyis la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5114: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5115: gshin rje gshed kyi phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5116: srog gcod pa'i gnas yin pas rna ba gnyis la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5117: ma tha ma tha h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5118: mi g.yo mgon po'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5119: rdzun tu smra ba'i gnas yin pas lce la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5121: rta mgrin gyi phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5122: ngag 'khyal ba'i gnas yin pas de yang lce la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5124: gzhan gyi mi thub pa'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5125: phra ma'i gnas yin pas gsang bar thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5127: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5128: tshig rtsub kyi gnas yin pas dpung pa g.yon pa thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5129: ka tam ka ye dza ye bi dza ye badz+ra /
NK009(ta)003:5130: khams gsum rnam rgyal gyi phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5131: gnod sems kyi gnas yin pas dpyi g.yas g.yon la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5132: a dzi te a pa ra dzi te badz+ra /
NK009(ta)003:5133: h'u ka ra'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5134: log par lta ba'i gnas yin par spyi gtsug tu thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5135: ma ra ya s+ya pra mar+d+ha na ye h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5136: stobs po che'i phur pa ste /
NK009(ta)003:5137: brnab sems spong ba'i gnas yin par rkang pa'i mthil du thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5138: de rnams kyis ni mi dge ba bcu rtsad nas
NK009(ta)003:5139: gcod pa'i phyir khro bo bcu'i phur pa lus kyi
NK009(ta)003:5141: de nas tshad med pa bzhi dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir //
NK009(ta)003:5142: sgo ma bzhi'i phur pa lus kyi mtsho bzhi la gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:5143: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya kun la 'gre /
NK009(ta)003:5144: bi ta ya bing bing h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5145: lcags kyu ma yi phur pa de glo snying dbugs kyi mtsho la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5146: na mahs man+ta hring hring h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5147: zhags pa ma yi pharu pa de mchin pa khrag gi mtsho la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5148: su ru su ru pra su ru h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5149: lcags sgrog ma yi phur pa de an stong du rus pa'i mtsho la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5150: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5151: dril bu ma'i phur pa de klad pa byang chub sems kyi mtsho la thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5152: de la pha rol du phyin pa drug dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK009(ta)003:5153: mi bzad pa'i phur pa drug gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:5154: ha sa ya ra h+r+ai da na ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5155: khrag gi gnad gcod pa seng ldeng gi phur pa spyi gtsug tu gdab pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:5156: a be sha ya a be sha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5157: dbugs kyi gnad gcod pa bya rgod kyi phur pa rkang mthil du thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5158: sh+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5159: 'byung bzhi'i gnad gcod pa mchog gi phur pa gsang ba'i gnas su thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5160: dz+wa la p+aa ya dz+wa la p+aa ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5161: rtsa bzhi'i gnad gcod pa tsan+dana gyi phur pa lce'i dkyil du thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5162: ta th+aa ya ta tha ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5163: tshe'i gnad gcod pa lcags kyi phur pa snying gi dkyil du thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5164: bi da ya bi da ya h'u phata /
NK009(ta)003:5165: phyi 'od kyi gnad gcod pa skyer pa'i phur pa lte bar thob cig /
NK009(ta)003:5166: de ltar yang rtsa rgyud las /
NK009(ta)003:5167: spyi bo'i gtsug tu gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5168: gnam gyi 'ju thag bcad pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:5169: rkang pa'i mthil du gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5170: sa yi rten phur phyung ba yin //
NK009(ta)003:5171: lce yi dkyil du gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5172: smra ba'i ngag rnams gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:5173: gsang ba'i gnas su gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5174: skye ba dgu brgyud bcas pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:5175: lte ba'i gnas la gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5176: bskyed pa'i sa bon gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:5177: dkar nag snying la gdab pa ni //
NK009(ta)003:5178: kun gzhi'i rnam shes gzhom pa yin //
NK009(ta)003:5180: de ltar phur pa nyi shu tham pa'o //
NK009(ta)003:5181: de nas thams cad kyi mjug tu sras mchog badz+ra
NK009(ta)003:5182: 'dus pa'i phur pa snying dkar nag gi mtshams su
NK009(ta)003:5183: gdab pa ni / phur pa la byug bdug byas te /
NK009(ta)003:5184: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana ban+d+ha h'u phata kyis gdab pa ni /
NK009(ta)003:5185: rnam par shes pa de len par byed pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:5186: tshe lung khrus lung ltar ro //
NK009(ta)003:5187: des gdab phur nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK009(ta)003:5188: de rnams ni rgyud kyi dgongs pa yin te /
NK009(ta)003:5189: yang rgyud sde kha cig nas /
NK009(ta)003:5191: gsung ltar gdab pa thugs ltar gdab par bya ba bshad pa yin /
NK009(ta)003:5192: gzhi smug nag la yod pa'i phur pa rnams sku ltar gdab par 'gro /
NK009(ta)003:5193: gzhi dmar nag la yod pa rnams gsung /
NK009(ta)003:5194: gzhi mthing nag la yod pa rnams thugs so //
NK009(ta)003:5199: las kyi gdab las bshad pa ni dal gyi phyogs nas bshad pa yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5200: yang rgyud sde kha cig las /
NK009(ta)003:5204: drag po'i gdab las zhes bshad pa'ang phur pa la phye ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5205: yang rgyud sde kha cig la /
NK009(ta)003:5206: dang po phur pa gcig gis sems kyi dbyings phyung /
NK009(ta)003:5207: gnyis pas kun gzhi rtsad nas bcad /
NK009(ta)003:5208: bcu bdun gyis byung tshor gyi sgo bkag /
NK009(ta)003:5209: nyi shu pas gnam gyi 'ju thag bcad /
NK009(ta)003:5210: rtsa gcig pas sa yi rten phur phyung bar bshad pa'ang gong ma la brtsis pas tshang ngo //
NK009(ta)003:5211: de yang spyi gdab las byas pas srog chags sems
NK009(ta)003:5212: can lta bu la snying rje med pas mtshon 'debs
NK009(ta)003:5213: pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK009(ta)003:5214: 'o na ci lta bu yin zhe na /
NK009(ta)003:5215: phur pa ni lhar bskyed pas thugs rje ye shes kyi ngo bo yin la /
NK009(ta)003:5216: gdab yul sems can de'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:5217: ma rig pa la btab pas las kyi sgrib pa
NK009(ta)003:5218: dang gnod sems dag nas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sgrol
NK009(ta)003:5220: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK009(ta)003:5222: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK009(ta)003:5224: gzhan don gyi ngo bo yin te /
NK009(ta)003:5225: gsang sngags kyi che ba yin no //
NK009(ta)003:5227: khog don drug pa mnan sreg 'phang gsum gyis las kyi mjug bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5231: dang po mnan gtad la gsang sngags kyi gzhung re
NK009(ta)003:5232: re'i rjes su 'brangs nas rang rang gi lugs mang
NK009(ta)003:5233: yang / zas skal du gtad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:5234: dgra skal du gtad pa dang /
NK009(ta)003:5235: grogs skal du gtad pa gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:5236: de re re la gsum gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5239: gzir te gtad pa gsum gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:5240: de re re la'ang gsum gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5243: nor bu lugs su gtad la gsum gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:5244: spyir gtad la mi btang pa gsum yod do //
NK009(ta)003:5248: gtad la phung pa rnam pa gsum yod de /
NK009(ta)003:5249: man ngag dang ldan na dgra phung /
NK009(ta)003:5250: srung ba med na rang phung /
NK009(ta)003:5251: dus tshod ma shes na rdzas phung ba'o //
NK009(ta)003:5255: gtad lam gtod pa gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:5260: gtad la gzhugs pa rnam pa gsum ste /
NK009(ta)003:5261: mtsho dang chu mig skams gsum mo //
NK009(ta)003:5264: lkug pa kha med gnam gyi mtsho /
NK009(ta)003:5266: long ba mig med mtsho de can la gtad /
NK009(ta)003:5268: smyon pa rwa med shing gi mtsho gsum kha shing rtsis bskor ba /
NK009(ta)003:5271: nag po ral gcig nags kyi chu /
NK009(ta)003:5273: dmar po rting khrol brag gi chu /
NK009(ta)003:5275: 'brong bu rwa sngon dar gyi chu /
NK009(ta)003:5276: mgo gnyis la rkang gcig tu song ba /
NK009(ta)003:5278: rgyal mtshan gyi rtse la gtad pa /
NK009(ta)003:5279: 'brong gi rwa dbrag tu gtad pa /
